h%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20note%20does%20not%20specify%20any%20specific%20mental%20or%20physical%20tests%20that%20were%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAronwald%20holds%20a%20degree%20in%20Osteopathic%20Medicine%2C%20which%20is%20a%20holistic%20approach%20to%20medicine%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebased%20on%20%26quot%3Blittle%20more%20than%20a%20pseudoscience%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fsciencebiz%2F2010%2F10%2F27%2Fosteopaths-versus-doctors%2F%3Fsh%3D31ccec661033%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20origins%20of%20osteopathic%20medicine%20began%20with%20the%20belief%20that%20manipulating%20the%20skeleton%20via%20massage%20could%20cure%20disease%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%20It%20has%20since%20expanded%20to%20include%20legitimate%20medical%20practices%2C%20though%20it%20is%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcgill.ca%2Foss%2Farticle%2Fmedical-health-and-nutrition%2Fosteopathy-needs-science-lend-hand%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregarded%20with%20skepticism%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20traditional%20medical%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20physical%20exams%20were%20well%20within%20the%20normal%20range%20and%20his%20cognitive%20exams%20were%20exceptional%2C%26quot%3B%20Aronwald's%20note%20reads.%20%26quot%3BIn%20addition%2C%20his%20most%20recent%20extensive%20laboratory%20analysis%20remains%20well%20within%20normal%20limits%20and%20was%20even%20more%20favorable%20than%20prior%20testing%20in%20some%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20parameters%2C%20most%20likely%20secondary%20to%20weight%20reduction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F111