candid%20in%20his%20communications%20with%20the%20board.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESustkever%20is%20said%20to%20have%20offered%20two%20explanations%20he%20purportedly%20received%20from%20the%20board%2C%20according%20to%20one%20of%20the%20people%20familiar.%20One%20explanation%20was%20that%20Altman%20was%20said%20to%20have%20given%20two%20people%20at%20OpenAI%20the%20same%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20was%20that%20Altman%20allegedly%20gave%20two%20board%20members%20different%20opinions%20about%20a%20member%20of%20personnel.%20An%20OpenAI%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20explanations%20didn't%20make%20sense%20to%20employees%20and%20were%20not%20received%20well%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20familiar%20said.%20Internally%2C%20the%20going%20theory%20is%20that%20this%20was%20a%20straightforward%20%26quot%3Bcoup%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20board%2C%20as%20it's%20been%20called%20inside%20the%20company%20and%20out.%20Any%20reason%20being%20given%20by%20the%20board%20now%20holds%20little%20to%20no%20sway%20with%20staff%2C%20the%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hours%20after%20that%20meeting%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-workers-threaten-to-quit-over-sam-altman-firing-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eopen%20letter%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20drafted%2C%20circulated%20among%20staff%20overnight%2C%20and%20signed%20by%20OpenAI%20leadership%20including%20Murati%20and%20Sutskever%2C%20in%20which%20they%20protested%20the%20board's%20decision%20to%20not%20bring%20Altman%20back.%20By%20mid-day%20Monday%2C%20it%20had%20been%20signed%20by%20over%2090%25%20of%20the%20employees%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20employees%20insisted%20they%20would%20resign%20if%20remaining%20members%20of%20board%20did%20not%2C%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbret-taylor-no-longer-s