Friday.%20Now%20that%20she's%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%20company%20should%20Altman%20not%20return%2C%20along%20with%20Sustkever%2C%20who%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Filyasut%2Fstatus%2F1726590052392956028%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epublicly%20expressed%20his%20%26quot%3Bregret%26quot%3B%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20board's%20move%20against%20Altman%2C%20some%20wonder%20if%20all%20these%20top%20players%20could%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20the%20OpenAI%20team%20and%20leadership%20elsewhere.%20Others%2C%20however%2C%20believe%20that%20Sustkever%20won't%20be%20easily%20forgiven%20and%20won't%20be%20invited%20to%20stay%2C%20or%20join%20a%20new%20venture%20at%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20an%20OpenAI%20employee%20or%20someone%20with%20a%20tip%20or%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20Kali%20Hays%20at%20khays%40insider.com%2C%20on%20secure%20messaging%20app%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsignal.org%2Fdownload%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESignal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20at%20949-280-0267%2C%20or%20through%20Twitter%20DM%20at%20%40hayskali.%20Reach%20out%20using%20a%20non-work%20device.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenais-employees-given-explanations-why-sam-altman-out-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700522118000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655b987f22cf74a5739a326f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenais-employees-given-explanations-why-sam-altman-out-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20a%20late%20Sunday%20meeting%2C%20Ilya%20Sutskever%20relayed%20two%20explanations%20for%20Altman's%20ouster.%20They%20are%20furious.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kali%20Hays)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canoni