is%20penchant%20for%20leaving%20work%20early%20to%20pursue%20interests%20in%20fashion%20design%20and%20yoga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%20Dorsey%20was%20reinstated%20as%20CEO%20in%202015%20and%20held%20the%20position%20for%20six%20years%20before%20resigning%20in%202021.%20Parag%20Agrawal%20took%20over%20as%20CEO%20following%20Mr%20Dorsey's%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETravis%20Kalanick%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUber's%20CEO%2C%20Travis%20Kalanick%2C%20stepped%20down%20from%20his%20position%20in%202017.%20His%20resignation%20came%20just%20a%20week%20after%20he%20had%20taken%20an%20indefinite%20leave%20of%20absence.%20The%20company%20was%20embroiled%20in%20a%20major%20crisis%20in%20February%20when%20a%20former%20employee%20published%20a%20blog%20post%20alleging%20widespread%20gender%20discrimination%20and%20sexual%20harassment%20within%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EJerry%20Yang%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYahoo%20Inc%20co-founder%20Jerry%20Yang%20stepped%20down%20in%202012%2C%20appeasing%20shareholders%20who%20had%20blasted%20the%20Internet%20pioneer%20for%20pursuing%20an%20ineffective%20personal%20vision%20and%20impeding%20investment%20deals%20that%20could%20have%20transformed%20the%20struggling%20company%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yang's%20abrupt%20departure%20comes%20two%20weeks%20after%20Yahoo%20appointed%20Scott%20Thompson%20as%20its%20new%20CEO%2C%20with%20a%20mandate%20to%20return%20the%20once-leading%20Internet%20portal%20to%20the%20heights%20it%20enjoyed%20in%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700502720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F4i2ugtf8_sam-altman-afp_625x300_18_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ffrom-sam-altman-to-steve-jobs-5-founders-who-were-fired-from-their-own-company-4590749%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Altman%20is%20not%20the%20only%20CEO%20who%20has%20been%20fired