on-as-russia-protests-closings-of-crossings%2Famp_articleshow%2F105364608.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ffinlands-prime-minister-hints-at-further-border-action-as-russia-protests-closings-of-crossings%2Famp_articleshow%2F105364608.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMore%20Than%20Children%2C%20It%20Is%20Parents...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20On%20Student%20Suicides%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIntense%20competition%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpressure%26quot%3B%20of%20parents%20on%20their%20wards%20preparing%20for%20competitive%20exams%20are%20the%20main%20reasons%20for%20the%20rising%20number%20of%20suicides%20across%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20a%20plea%20that%20sought%20regulation%20of%20the%20mushrooming%20coaching%20institutes%20and%20cited%20the%20data%20on%20student%20suicides%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20SVN%20Bhatti%2C%20however%2C%20expressed%20helplessness%20and%20said%20the%20judiciary%20cannot%20pass%20directions%20in%20such%20a%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20not%20easy%20things.%20Pressure%20from%20parents%20is%20behind%20all%20these%20incidents.%20More%20than%20the%20children%2C%20it%20is%20the%20parents%20who%20are%20putting%20pressure%20on%20them.%20How%20can%20the%20court%20pass%20directions%20in%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20told%20advocate%20Mohini%20Priya%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20petitioner%20-%20Mumbai-based%20doctor%20Aniruddha%20Narayan%20Malpani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAlthough%2C%20most%20of%20us%20will%20not%20want%20any%20coaching%20institute%20to%20be%20there%2C%20but%20look%20at%20the%20conditions%20of%20schools.%20There%20is%20intense%20competition%20and%20students%20have%20no%20other%20option%20but%20to%20go%20to%20these%20coaching%20institutes.%26quot%3B%20Referring%20to%20the%202020%20data%20of%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%2C%20Priya%20said%20it%20highlights%20that%20around%208.2%20per%20cent%20of%20students%20in%20the%20country%20die%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20it%20knows%20about%20the%20situation%20but%20the%20court%20can't%20pass%20directions%20and%20suggested%20that%20the%20petitioner%20instead%20approach%20the%20government%20with%20his%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriya%20sought%20to%20withdraw%20the%20plea%20to%20approach%20the%20appropriate%20forum%2C%20which%20the%20court%20allowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20filed%20by%20Malpani%20through%20Priya%20said%20that%20it%20seeks%20appropriate%20directions%20for%20regulating%20the%20conduct%20of%20%E2%80%9Cprofit-hungry%20private%20coaching%20institutes%20mushrooming%20across%20India%20which%20provide%20coaching%20for%20various%20competitive%20entrance%20examinations%20such%20as%20IIT-JEE%20(Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20Joint%20Entrance%20Examination)%20and%20NEET%20(National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20petitioner%20has%20been%20constrained%20to%20approach%20the%20court%20as%20several%20students%20have%20committed%20suicides%20in%20recent%20years%20%26quot%3Bfacilitated%20by%20the%20absolute%20lack%20of%20regulation%20and%20oversight%20by%20the%20Respondents%20(Centre%20and%20state%20governments)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChildren%20as%20young%20as%2014%20years%20enter%20these%20coaching%20factories%20often%20away%20from%20their%20homes%20and%20undergo%20rigorous%20preparation%20in%20the%20anticipation%20of%20getting%20admission%20to%20a%20good%20medical%20or%20engineering%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20being%20in%20a%20protected%20home%20environment%2C%20the%20child%20is%20suddenly%20exposed%20to%20the%20harsh%20competitive%20world%20without%20being%20mentally%20equipped%20to%20do%20so.%20These%20profit-hungry%20coaching%20institutes%2C%20however%2C%20do%20not%20care%20about%20student%20well-being%20and%20are%20only%20focussed%20on%20minting%20money%20leading%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20India%20being%20pressurised%20enough%20to%20take%20their%20own%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20children%20are%20being%20made%20to%20live%20and%20study%20in%20these%20coaching%20factories%20in%20subpar%20and%20abnormal%20conditions%20which%20are%20severely%20affecting%20their%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20most%20dangerous%20about%20mental%20health%20is%20that%20it%20is%20invisible%2C%20unlike%20other%20ailments%20in%20our%20body.%20However%2C%20just%20like%20other%20physical%20ailments%2C%20mental%20health%20problems%20too%20are%20triggered%20by%20extrinsic%20forces%2C%20surrounding%20environment%20and%20pressures%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20said%20that%20student%20suicides%20were%20a%20grave%20human%20rights%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lackadaisical%20attitude%20of%20the%20Centre%20in%20enacting%20a%20law%20despite%20the%20rising%20number%20of%20suicides%20clearly%20reflects%20upon%20the%20State's%20apathy%20towards%20protecting%20these%20young%20minds%20who%20are%20the%20future%20of%20our%20country%20and%20their%20constitutional%20right%20to%20live%20with%20dignity%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%2021%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20plea%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700500620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fgv8pfg28_supreme-court_625x300_04_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparental-pressure-behind-student-suicides-supreme-courts-big-remark-4590202%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIntense%20