Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20players%20who%20have%20been%20picked%2C%20the%20performances%20of%20the%20likes%20of%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Tilak%20Varma%20and%20Rinku%20Singh%20will%20be%20closely%20watched%20as%20India%20begin%20a%20phase%20where%20they%20would%20want%20to%20give%20fresh%20faces%20a%20chance%2C%20with%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20a%20year%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20bowlers%20are%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20Avesh%20Khan%2C%20Mukesh%20Kumar%20and%20Ravi%20Bishnoi.%20All%20of%20them%20have%20enough%20experience%20in%20T20s%20and%20have%20played%20for%20India.%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Washington%20Sundar%20and%20Shivam%20Dubey%20are%20the%20all-rounders%20in%20the%20squad.%20Jitesh%20Sharma%20is%20the%20back-up%20wicketkeeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20selected%20stars%20have%20been%20star%20performers%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%20With%20the%20BCCI%20selectors%20showing%20an%20inclination%20to%20give%20the%20younger%20lot%20a%20longer%20rope%20in%20the%20T20I%20format%2C%20the%20selected%20players%20would%20be%20eager%20to%20seal%20their%20spot%20for%20a%20longer%20duration%20with%20next%20year's%20T20%20World%20up%20in%20focus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIndia's%20squad%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%20(Captain)%2C%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20(vice-captain)%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Tilak%20Varma%2C%20Rinku%20Singh%2C%20Jitesh%20Sharma%20(wk)%2C%20Washington%20Sundar%2C%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Shivam%20Dubey%2C%20Ravi%20Bishnoi%2C%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20Prasidh%20Krishna%2C%20Avesh%20Khan%2C%20Mukesh%20Kumar.%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20will%20join%20the%20squad%20as%20vice-captain%20for%20the%20last%20two%20T20Is%20in%20Raipur%20and%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Agency%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700499840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fse0gvu5_suryakumar-yadav-_625x300_02_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcr