ing%20to%20PTI.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20sent%20the%20pipe%2053%20metres%20to%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20rubble%20and%20the%20trapped%20workers%20can%20hear%20and%20experience%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fbig-story%2Fpipeline-pushed-through-rubble-breakthrough-at-collapsed-uttarakhand-tunnel-boosts-morale%2F692047.html%5C%22%3EPTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20send%20food%2C%20mobile%2C%20and%20charger%20to%20the%20people%20who%20are%20trapped%20inside%20the%20tunnel.%20We%20will%20also%20try%20to%20install%20a%20WiFi%20connection%20inside.%20DRDO%20robots%20are%20also%20working%2C%E2%80%9D%20NHIDCL%20General%20Manager%20Colonel%20Deeapk%20Patil%2C%20who%20is%20heading%20the%20rescue%20efforts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1726615871546892766%5C%22%3Etold%20ANI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20tunnelling%20expert%20Arnold%20Dix%2C%20who%20has%20been%20roped%20in%20for%20the%20rescue%20efforts%20by%20authorities%2C%20expressed%20satisfaction%20at%20the%20efforts%20so%20far%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fbig-story%2Fpipeline-pushed-through-rubble-breakthrough-at-collapsed-uttarakhand-tunnel-boosts-morale%2F692047.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20PTI.%20He%20called%20the%20progress%20between%20yesterday%20and%20today%20%E2%80%9Cextraordinary%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20just%20been%20down%20in%20the%20tunnel%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dix%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Geneva-based%20International%20Tunnelling%20and%20Underground%20Space%20Association%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20Monday.%20%E2%80%9CEnormous%20amount%20of%20work%20has%20been%20done%20there%20in%20preparation%2C%20and%20we%20are%20just%20coming%20up%20here%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20mountain%20to%20consider%20other%20options%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20timeline%20yet%3B%20opposition%20asks%20for%20CBI%20inquiry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Dix%20did%20not%20give%20a%20timeline%20for%20the%20rescue%2C%20reported%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Assembly%20Yashpal%20Arya%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20also%20visited%20the%20site%20on%20Monday%20but%20was%20not%20allowed%20inside%20the%20tunnel%2C%20reported%20PTI.%20Arya%20has%20demanded%20a%20CBI%20inquiry%20monitored%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Uttarakhand%20High%20Court%20to%20find%20out%20if%20the%20execution%20of%20the%20project%20was%20given%20to%20an%20inexperienced%20firm%20and%20if%20that%20led%20to%20the%20disaster%2C%20PTI%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fbig-story%2Fpipeline-pushed-through-rubble-breakthrough-at-collapsed-uttarakhand-tunnel-boosts-morale%2F692047.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20options%20being%20considered%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20PTI%2C%20authorities%20are%20also%20looking%20at%20another%20option%20of%20drilling%20more%20than%2080%20metres%20down%20into%20the%20hill%20to%20reach%20the%20workers.%20A%20road%20has%20been%20laid%20for%20heavy%20drilling%20machinery%20used%20by%20the%20Oil%20and%20Natural%20Gas%20Corporation%20(ONGC)%20to%20be%20transported%20to%20the%20top%2C%20per%20the%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1978314%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20evening%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%2C%20the%20first%20machine%20of%20the%20Satluj%20Jal%20Vidyut%20Nigam%20Limited%20(SJVNL%2C%20a%20Central%20Public%20Sector%20Enterprise%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Power)%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20vertical%20rescue%20tunnel%20has%20already%20reached%20the%20tunnel%20site%20and%20operations%20are%20being%20commenced%20post%