%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700496953000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105363890%2Cimgsize-29756.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Finternational-emmy-awards-2023-live-updates-shefali-shah-vir-das-jim-sarb-succession-emmy-awards-winners-2023%2Fliveblog%2F105363890.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105363890.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amway%20Faces%20Legal%20Action%20In%20Rs%204%2C050%20Crore%20Alleged%20Money%20Laundering%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20(ED)%20has%20filed%20a%20prosecution%20complaint%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%2C%202002%20against%20Amway%20India%20Enterprise%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20(Amway).%20The%20complaint%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20the%20Court%20of%20the%20Hon'ble%20Metropolitan%20Sessions%20Judge%20cum%20Special%20Court%20(PMLA)%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20which%20took%20cognizance%20of%20the%20matter%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20investigation%20stems%20from%20various%20FIRs%20registered%20by%20the%20Telangana%20Police%20against%20Amway%20and%20its%20Directors%20under%20different%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20suggest%20that%20Amway%20engaged%20in%20promoting%20an%20illegal%20'Money%20Circulation%20Scheme'%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20selling%20goods%2C%20deceiving%20the%20public%20by%20promising%20high%20commissions%20and%20incentives%20through%20simple%20enrolment%20of%20new%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ED's%20findings%2C%20Amway%20has%20been%20operating%20a%20Pyramid%20scheme%20masquerading%20as%20direct%20selling.%20Instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20the%20direct%20sale%20of%20goods%20to%20end%20consumers%2C%20Amway%20introduced%20a%20multi-level%20marketing%20scheme%20with%20numerous%20intermediaries%20in%20the%20form%20of%20distributors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme's%20survival%20relies%20heavily%20on%20enrolling%20new%20members%2C%20with%20commissions%20and%20incentives%20increasing%20for%20those%20higher%20up%20in%20the%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20contends%20that%20Amway's%20activities%20constitute%20a%20Multi-Level%20Marketing%20Scheme%20and%20Money%20Circulation%20Scheme%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20generation%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20amounting%20to%20Rs%204050.21%20Crore%20through%20the%20scheduled%20offence%20of%20cheating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20investigation%20uncovered%20that%20over%20Rs%202%2C859%20crore%20collected%20from%20members%20was%20allegedly%20siphoned%20off%20and%20transferred%20to%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20overseas%20investors%2C%20disguised%20as%20dividends%2C%20royalties%2C%20and%20other%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20enforcement%20measures%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20attached%20movable%20and%20immovable%20properties%20valued%20at%20Rs%20757.77%20Crore%20in%20connection%20with%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20is%20ongoing%2C%20and%20the%20ED%20continues%20to%20delve%20into%20the%20complex%20financial%20dealings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmway's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20ED's%20prosecution%2C%20Amway%20India%20issued%20a%20statement%20through%20its%20spokesperson%2C%20addressing%20the%20investigation%20that%20dates%20back%20to%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmway%20India%20Spokesperson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Prosecution%20Complaint%20currently%20filed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20pertains%20to%20the%20investigation%20dating%20back%20to%202011%20and%20since%20then%20we%20have%20been%20cooperating%20with%20the%20department%20and%20have%20shared%20all%20the%20information%20as%20sought%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20Since%20Amway%20began%20its%20operations%20in%20India%2025%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20has%20been%20committed%20to%20legal%20and%20regulatory%20compliance%20and%20has%20diligently%20maintained%20a%20culture%20of%20compliance%20and%20integrity%20to%20the%20present%20day.%20We%20want%20to%20reiterate%20our%20continued%20confidence%20in%20the%20Indian%20legal%20and%20judicial%20system%20following%20the%20due%20process%20of%20law%20as%20we%20pursue%20our%20legal%20rights.%20Amway%20is%20proud%20of%20its%20rich%20history%20in%20India%20and%20will%20vigorously%20defend%20itself%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20over%202%2C500%20employees%20and%20over%205.5%20lakh%20independent%20distributors%20who%20are%20critical%20to%20its%20mission%20of%20helping%20people%20live%20healthier%2C%20better%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20asserted%20its%20cooperation%20with%20the%20department%2C%20sharing%20all%20required%20information%20throughout%20the%20process.%20The%20spokesperson%20reiterated%20Amway's%20commitment%20to%20legal%20and%20regulatory%20compliance%2C%20emphasizing%20a%20culture%20of%20integrity%20and%20compliance%20since%20its%20establishment%20in%20India%2025%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmway%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20the%20Indian%20legal%20and%20judicial%20system%2C%20pledging%20to%20follow%20due%20process%20and%20defend%20itself%20vigorously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20legal%20challenges%2C%20Amway%20remains%20proud%20of%20its%20history%20in%20India%20and%20stands%20firm%20in%20its%20mission%20to%20support%20over%202%2C500%20employees%20and%20more%20than%205.5%20lakh%20independent%20distributors%2C%20aiming%20to%20contribute%20to%20healthier%20and%20better%20lives%20for%20people%20across%20the%20country%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20affirms%20its%20dedication%20to%20pursuing%20legal%20rights%20while%20navigating%20through%20the%20legal%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700496360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2Fm63u8rbk_amway-website_625x300_18_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famway-faces-legal-action-in-rs-4-050-crore-alleged-money-laundering-case-4590507%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20(ED)%20has%20filed%20a%20prosecution%20complaint%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%2C%202002%20against%20Amway%20India%20Enterprise%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20(Amway).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famway-faces-legal-action-in-rs-4-050-crore-alleged-money-laundering-case-4590507%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famway-faces-legal-action-in-rs-4-050-crore-alleged-money-laundering-case-4590507%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famway-faces-legal-action-in-rs-4-050-crore-alleged-money-laundering-case-4590507%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Andhra%20Pradesh%20HC%20Gives%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20Bail%20in%20Skill%20Development%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F24143246%2Fnaidu.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20high%20court%20on%20Monday%20(November%2020)%20granted%20regular%20bail%20to%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20chief%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20in%20the%20skill%20development%20scam%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20T.%20Mallikarjun%20Rao%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fchandrababu-naidu-bail-skill-development-scam-andhra-pradesh-high-court-242592%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20from%20the%20material%20on%20the%20record%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20definitively%20concluded%20that%20the%20misappropriated%20amounts%20were%20diverted%20to%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%E2%80%99s%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20petitioner%2C%20A.37%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20September%209%2C%202023%2C%20and%20remained%20in%20judicial%20custody%20until%20being%20granted%20interim%20bail%20on%20health%20grounds%20on%20October%2031%2C%202023%2C%20following%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20orders.%20Despite%20allegations%20of%20transferring%20misappropriated%20amounts%20to%20the%20T.D.P.%20party%E2%80%99s%20account%2C%20no%20prima%20facie%20evidence%20is%20presented%20to%20support%20this%20claim.%20This%20court%20views%20that%20such%20serious%20allegations%20should%20be%20backed%20by%20substantial%20material%20before%20seeking%20the%20remand%20of%20the%20petitioner.%20The%20court%2C%20at%20this%20point%2C%20views%20the%20lack%20of%20supportive%20material%20as%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20investigation%E2%80%99s%20conclusion%20that%20the%20alleged%20misappropriated%20amount%20had%20been%20transferred%20to%20the%20T.D.P.%20party%E2%80%99s%20account.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20Naidu%20could%20not%20be%20held%20responsible%20for%20all%20the%20discrepancies%20noted%20in%20the%20forensic%20audit%20report%20as%20per%20which%20out%20of%20the%20Rs%20371%20crore%2C%20at%20least%20Rs%20241%20crore%20were%20misappropriated%20by%20SISW%20and%20Design%20Tech%20and%20diverted%20to%20various%20shell%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Prosecution%20needs%20to%20clarify%20how%20the%20petitioner%20can%20be%20held%20responsible%20for%20such%20discrepancies%2C%20as%20it%20is%20not%20his%20duty%2C%20as%20the%20then%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20to%20verify%20and%20compare%20parties%E2%80%99%20signatures%E2%80%A6It%20remains%20to%20be%20clarified%20how%20the%20differences%20outlined%20in%20the%20report%20can%20be%20deemed%20the%20fundamental%20cause%20for%20the%20alleged%20misappropriation%20of%20funds%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20October%2031%2C%20the%20court%20had%20granted%20Naidu%20four%20weeks%E2%80%99%20medical%20bail.%20He%20had%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20CID%20on%20September%209%20and%20has%20been%20in%20the%20Rajahmundry%20central%20prison%20since%20September%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CID%20has%20listed%20Naidu%20as%20%E2%80%98accused%20number%20one%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20alleged%20skill%20development%20scam.%20He%20is%20charged%20with%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20cheating%2C%20forgery%2C%20breach%20of%20trust%2C%20destruction%20of%20evidence%2C%20and%20abetment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20reported%20that%20the%20scam%20is%20allegedly%20a%20Rs%20279-crore%20one.%20The%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fandhrapradesh%2Fap-cid-chief-n-sanjay-seems-to-have-a-penchant-for-prosecuting-chandrababu-naidu-and-his-relatives%2F%5C%22%3Enews%20outlet%20has%20also%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20CID%20chief%20N%20Sanjay%E2%80%99s%20run-ins%20with%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20kin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP%20leaders%20Kaluva%20Srinivasulu%2C%20Bhuma%20Brahmananda%20Reddy%2C%20A.V.%20Subba%20Reddy%2C%20B.C.%20Janardhan%20Reddy%20and%20Akhila%20Priya%20were%20also%20arrested%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%20has%20claimed%20that%20this%20case%20is%20an%20act%20of%20political%20vendetta%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700496198000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F24143246%2Fn