be%20very%20premature%20of%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20to%20transfer%20the%20money%2C%20more%20so%20since%20the%20process%20of%20transferring%20via%20the%20Sahara%20refund%20portal%20is%20still%20going%20on%2C%20said%20government%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20managed%20to%20pay%20about%20Rs%20230%20crore%20to%20as%20many%20as%202.5%20lakh%20investors.%20New%20registrations%20are%20still%20taking%20place%2C%20so%20it%20would%20be%20premature%20to%20say%20money%20from%20the%20SEBI%20would%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20Consolidated%20Fund%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%20has%20been%20transferring%20money%20from%20the%20funds%20lying%20the%20SEBI%20within%2045%20days%20of%20registrations%20after%20being%20verified%20on%20the%20refund%20portal%20which%20was%20launched%20by%20Union%20Co-operative%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20last%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Roy%20started%20facing%20problems%20in%202012%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20upheld%20a%20SEBI%20order%20instructing%20the%20Sahara%20India%20Real%20Estate%20Corp%20and%20Sahara%20Housing%20Investment%20Corp%20to%20repay%20their%20investors%20with%20interest.%20The%20court%20had%20then%20asked%20for%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20to%20be%20invested%20with%20the%20SEBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20had%20asked%20these%20companies%20to%20deposit%20the%20money%20with%20the%20SEBI%2C%20but%20since%20they%20did%20not%20have%20cash%2C%20they%20raised%20Rs%2080%2C000%20crore%20via%20four%20co-operative%20societies.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%20Rs%2025000%20crore%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20SEBI%20and%20Sahara%20Group%20invested%20the%20remaining%20amount%20in%20Aamby%20Valley%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20claimed%20that%20they%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20when%20the%20retail%20investors%20who%20had%20deposited%20money%20with%20the%20cooperative%20societies%20wanted%20their%20money%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20court's%20guidance%2C%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20was%20initially%20transferred%20from%20the%20SEBI%20and%20investors%20started%20getting%20money%20via%20the%20Sahara%20refund%20portal.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20further%20need%2C%20the%20government%20would%20ask%20SEBI%20to%20transfer%20more%20money%20to%20the%20refund%20portal%2C%20according%20to%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20automated%2C%20streamlined%2C%20and%20structured%20process%20and%20it%20is%20still%20ongoing.%20Once%20completed%2C%20then%20only%20the%20legality%20of%20transferring%20the%20funds%20to%20CFI%20can%20be%20examined%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20transfer%20would%20also%20include%20the%20provision%20of%20transferring%20funds%20to%20investors%20in%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%202.76%20crore%20depositors%20had%20invested%20in%20four%20Co-operative%20societies%20and%2097%20percent%20of%20them%20were%20retail%20investors%20who%20deposited%20less%20than%20Rs%2040%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20records%20suggest%20most%20of%20the%20investors%20were%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar.%20Around%2085%20lakh%20investors%20from%20UP%20had%20deposited%20Rs%202%2C200%20crore%20and%2055%20lakh%20from%20Bihar%20deposited%20Rs%201%2C500%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubrata%20Roy%20died%20in%20Mumbai%20last%20Tuesday%20at%20the%20age%20of%2075%20after%20battling%20a%20prolonged%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700495340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fijsje7l_sahara-chief-subrata-roy-650_625x300_31_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-government-benefit-from-saharas-rs-25-000-crore-undistributed-funds-4590402%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sahara%20Group%20founder%20Subrata%20Roy's%20death%20last%20week%20brought%20to%20focus%20the%20undistribu