te%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20most%20trolled%20Indian%20cricketer%20in%20the%20last%2012%20months%20is%20the%20man%20standing%20up%20for%20the%20team%20when%20it%20mattered%20the%20most.%20The%20World%20Cup%20final.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWell%20played%2C%20Kamaal%20Lajwaab%20Rahul%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndvAus%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23IndvAus%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FCWC23Final%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23CWC23Final%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Aakash%20Chopra%20(%40cricketaakash)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcricketaakash%2Fstatus%2F1726195832775733291%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2011%20matches%2C%20KL%20scored%20452%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2075.33%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%2090.76.%20KL%20scored%20a%20century%20and%20two%20half-centuries%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20102.%20KL%20hit%20India's%20fastest%20World%20Cup%20century%20ever%20against%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20coming%20in%20just%2062%20balls.%20He%20is%20currently%20the%20eighth-highest%20run-scorer%20in%20the%20tournament.%20He%20along%20with%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20(530%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2066.25%2C%20with%20two%20centuries%20and%20three%20fifties%20in%2011%20matches)%20have%20been%20the%20pillars%20of%20Indian%20batting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKL%20has%20been%20in%20terrific%20form%20in%20ODIs%20this%20year%20as%20a%20middle-order%20batter.%20In%2024%20ODIs%20and%2022%20innings%2C%20he%20has%20scored%20983%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2070.21%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%2088.63%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20111*.%20He%20has%20scored%20two%20centuries%20and%20six%20fifties%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20Australia%20opted%20to%20bowl%20first