some%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Congress%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidered%20a%20%26quot%3Byouth%20icon%26quot%3B%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20is%20often%20greeted%20with%20chants%20of%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20you%26quot%3B%20during%20rallies.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20unadulterated%20type%20of%20outpouring%20that%20I%20receive%20sometimes%20from%20people%20who%20like%20what%20I%20do%20and%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20about%20work-life%20balance%20and%20how%20it%20gets%20disrupted%20during%20elections%3A%20%26quot%3BMy%20children%20are%20very%20sensible.%20They%20know%20it's%20election%20times%2C%20so%2C%20they%20didn't%20complain%20that%20I%20wasn't%20there%20for%20the%20Diwali%20holidays.%20But%20I%20did%20spend%20a%20day%20with%20them%20and%20celebrated%20Diwali.%20Election%20will%20happen%20but%20it's%20also%20important%20to%20celebrate%20festivals%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20busy%20but%20one%20needs%20to%20make%20time.%20That%20balance%20is%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2046-year-old%20who%20likes%20watching%20movies%20during%20his%20free%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%20sees%20himself%20at%20the%20national%20level%20or%20in%20Rajasthan%20in%20the%20future%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20high%20command%20will%20decide%20that%20but%20my%20heart%20is%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Rajasthan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20spike%20in%20the%20Kota%20suicide%20cases%20this%20year%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20-%20father%20of%20two%20boys%20-%20said%20the%20society%20needs%20to%20%26quot%3Bchill%20and%20relax%20a%20bit%20and%20shouldn't%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20youth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20is%20going%20to%20polls%20on%20November%2025%20and%20Sachin%20Pilot%20is%20confident%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bwill%20win%20from%20his%20constituency%20Tonk%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20got%20the%20highest%20margin%20l