ver%20Failure%20to%20Clear%20Appointment%20of%20Two%20Sikh%20Lawyers%20as%20HC%20Judges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20185453%2FScreenshot-2023-11-20-at-6.53.34%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%2C%20November%2020%2C%20pulled%20up%20the%20Union%20government%20over%20the%20non-appointment%20of%20two%20Sikh%20lawyers%20as%20high%20court%20judges%2C%20once%20again%20noting%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpick%20and%20choose%E2%80%9D%20approach%20to%20the%20transfer%20and%20appointment%20of%20judges%20will%20create%20%E2%80%9Cembarrassing%20outcomes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fsupreme-court-questions-centre-non-appointment-two-sikh-candidates-high-court-judges%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%20and%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20referred%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20clear%20the%20names%20of%20advocates%20Harmeet%20Singh%20Grewal%20and%20Deepinder%20Singh%20Nalwa%20for%20appointment%20as%20judges%20of%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court.%20The%20duo%20was%20among%20five%20lawyers%20who%20were%20recommended%20for%20appointment%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Collegium%20on%20October%2017.%20On%20November%202%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20notified%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20three%20others%20but%20not%20Grewal%20and%20Nalwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20of%20the%20candidates%20not%20cleared%20are%20both%20Sikhs.%20Why%20should%20this%20arise%3F%20Don%E2%80%99t%20let%20past%20issues%20link%20up%20with%20present%20pending%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Kaul%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20told%20attorney%20general%20R.%20Venakataramani%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpick%20and%20choose%E2%80%9D%20policy%20does%20not%20create%20a%20good%20impression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20AG%20said%20the%20delay%20was%20due%20to%20elections%20and%20that%20progress%20has%20been%20made%20regarding%20the%20reiterated%20candidates%2C%20the%20top%20court%20observed%20that%20not%20even%2050%25%20of%20the%20names%20were%20cleared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsc-cautions-centre-that-selective-appointments-transfers-risk-embarrassing-outcomes%2Farticle67554083.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%C2%A0Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20also%20warned%20that%20such%20a%20policy%20could%20lead%20to%20%E2%80%9Cembarrassing%E2%80%9D%20outcomes%20such%20as%20deferring%20the%20swearing-in%20of%20new%20judges%20or%20withdrawing%20judges%20from%20judicial%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20will%20happen%20at%20some%20stage%20is%20we%20cannot%20let%20judges%20whom%20we%20do%20not%20want%20to%20work%20in%20a%20court%20to%20continue%20to%20work%20in%20that%20court%E2%80%A6%20Please%20do%20not%20let%20that%20happen.%20It%20will%20dilute%20the%20authority%20of%20judges.%20It%20will%20embarrass%20these%20judges%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Kaul%20told%20the%20AG%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20deferred%20the%20swearing-in%20of%20lawyer%20Kaushik%20Goswami%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20court.%20The%20government%20did%20not%20clear%20the%20name%20of%20N.%20Unni%20Krishnan%20Nair%2C%20who%20was%20also%20recommended%20for%20judgeship%20by%20the%20collegium%2C%20but%20as%20Goswami%E2%80%99s%20senior.%20The%20government%20only%20cleared%20Goswami%E2%80%99s%20appointment.%20After%20the%20high%20court%20deferred%20the%20swearing-in%20of%20Goswami%2C%20the%20government%20appointed%20Nair%20two%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20noted%20once%20again%20on%20Monday%20that%20if%20a%20candidate%20does%20not%20know%20what%20seniority%20he%20or%20she%20would%20get%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20persuade%20other%20eligible%20and%20deserving%20candidates%20to%20join%20the%20bench%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Dushyant%20Dave%2C%20for%20the%20petitioners%2C%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20should%20issue%20a%20mandamus%20to%20the%20government%20to%20clear%20all%20the%20pending%20names%20within%20the%20next%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20AG%20assured%20the%20court%20of%20action%2C%20the%20matter%20was%20listed%20for%20hearing%20on%20December%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20the%20Advocates%20Association%20Bengaluru%20over%20delays%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collegium%20and%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20tussle%20over%20the%20appointment%20and%20transfers%20of%20judges.%20The%20government%20has%20frequently%20refused%20to%20clear%20names%20recommended%20by%20the%20collegium.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-collegium-judges-appointment-centre-pick-and-choose%5C%22%3EExperts%20believe%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20this%20has%20undermined%20the%20collegium%E2%80%99s%20power%20and%20has%20allowed%20the%20government%20to%20indirectly%20influence%20judicial%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700488819000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20185453%2FScreenshot-2023-11-20-at-6.53.34%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-union-govt-failure-clear-appointment-two-sikh-lawyers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Harmeet%20Singh%20Grewal%20and%20Deepinder%20Singh%20Nalwa%20were%20among%20five%20lawyers%20recommended%20by%20the%20collegium%20for%20appointment%20as%20judges%20of%20the%20Punjab%20