t%20loud%2C%20even%20if%20the%20overwhelming%20majority%20had%20gone%20silent.%20The%20defeat%20had%20left%20them%20speechless%2C%20the%20Australian%20celebrations%20blind.%20In%20this%20collective%20expression%20of%20mourning%2C%20they%20had%20forgotten%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20superior%20skills%20and%20brilliant%20tactics%20of%20the%20rival%20team.%20It%20was%20as%20if%20not%20only%20had%20the%20invincibility%20of%20this%20Indian%20team%20been%20shattered%20but%20the%20very%20essence%20of%20their%20own%20identity%20had%20been%20ripped%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20362px)%2085vw%2C%20362px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22362%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750.jpg%20976w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750-244x300.jpg%20244w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750-833x1024.jpg%20833w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22445%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20match%2C%20I%20was%20at%20a%20television%20news%20debate%20on%20whether%20this%20was%20the%20best%20white-ball%20team%20India%20has%20ever%20had.%20The%20consensus%20was%20yes%2C%20it%20is.%20I%20met%20a%20wealthy%20Indian%20cricket%20fan%2C%20there%20for%20one%20of%20the%20many%20debates%20the%20news%20channel%20had%20lined%20up%20on%20the%20World%20Cup%20final.%20I%20presume%20he%20was%20wealthy%20because%20he%20had%20bought%20the%20cricket%20bat%20with%20which%20Dhoni%20hit%20the%20six%20that%20won%20the%202011%20World%20Cup.%20He%20had%20spent%201%20lakh%20pounds%20(around%20Rs%201%20crore)%20to%20acquire%20that%20memorabilia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20been%20to%20most%20World%20Cup%20finals%20and%20was%20now%20making%20plans%20to%20go%20to%20Ahmedabad.%20He%20was%20aware%20that%20tickets%20were%20selling%20in%20black%20for%20more%20than%20Rs%201%20lakh%20each%20and%20hotels%20were%20beyond%20the%20common%20man%E2%80%99s%20reach.%20He%20was%20sure%20India%20had%20the%20best%20chance%20now%20to%20add%20to%20the%20two%20World%20Cups%20it%20has%20already%20won%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20because%20the%20Indian%20team%20is%20strong%2C%20but%20also%20because%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20inspirational%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20touching%20faith%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20infallibility%20and%20the%20Indian%20team%20reminded%20me%20of%20a%20cricket%20fan%20I%20had%20met%20after%20India%20had%20decimated%20Afghanistan%20in%20Delhi.%20He%20was%20not%20worried%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20chances%20as%20he%20was%20sure%20India%20would%20be%20in%20the%20final%20at%20Ahmedabad%20and%20to%20defeat%20the%20team%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20state%20was%20an%20impossibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20seen%20the%20steam%20billowing%20out%20of%20the%20collective%20energy%20of%20the%20thousands%20that%20day%20inside%20the%20Jaitley%20stadium%20and%20had%20wondered%20how%20they%20would%20react%20to%20an%20Indian%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20remembered%20the%201996%20World%20Cup%20semifinals%20at%20the%20Eden%20Gardens%20in%20Kolkata.%20The%20advertising%20blitz%20around%20the%20Indian%20campaign%20convinced%20people%20that%20the%20cup%20and%20India%20are%20made%20for%20each%20other.%20On%20that%20night%2C%20the%20Eden%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Paradise%20that%20the%20fans%20had%20envisaged%20%E2%80%93%20turned%20into%20an%20inferno%20as%20the%20Indian%20batting%20collapsed%20against%20the%20eventual%20winners%20Sri%20Lanka.%20The%20angry%20crowds%20went%20berserk%2C%20the%20sky%20lit%20up%20with%20fire%20as%20newspapers%20were%20lit%20and%20the%20ground%20was%20showered%20with%20litter.%20The%20match%20was%20abandoned%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20way%20ahead%20of%20the%20Indians%2C%20were%20declared%20the%20victors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2023%20is%20no%201996.%20A%20cricket%20fan%20is%20now%20a%20greater%20political%20animal%20and%20his%20belief%20of%20invincibility%20stems%20from%20reasons%20beyond%20cricket.%20In%20this%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20even%20sports%20seem%20an%20extension%20of%20a%20narrative%20where%20the%20lines%20between%20self-belief%20and%20self-delusion%20have%20become%20blurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20thousands%20marched%20into%20the%20Ahmedabad%20stadium%20on%20Sunday%2C%20November%2019%2C%20they%20were%20convinced%20that%20cricket%20and%20their%20political%20leadership%20had%20aligned%20the%20stars%20so%20perfectly%20that%20defeat%20was%20an%20unthinkable%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20had%20other%20ideas.%20They%20had%20studied%20and%20dissected%20the%20Indian%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%20to%20perfection.%20They%20had%20even%20assessed%20the%20pitch%20conditions%20and%20the%20psychology%20of%20the%20highly%20partisan%20crowd%20well.%20What%20they%20unleashed%20on%20India%20was%20an%20exhibition%20of%20skills%2C%20planning%20and%20strategy%20that%20wore%20down%20a%20strong%20Indian%20team%20who%20despite%20their%20undeniable%20brilliance%20were%20yet%20to%20be%20really%20tested%20in%20their%20very%20vulnerable%20moments.%20To%20borrow%20from%20boxing%20terminology%2C%20Australia%20sparred%20first%20and%20once%20Indian%20defences%20were%20exposed%2C%20they%20unleashed%20a%20barrage%20of%20punches%20that%20left%20their%20opponents%20shell-shocked.%20Panic%20and%20pressure%2C%20something%20the%20Indians%20had%20appeared%20immune%20to%20so%20far%2C%20surfaced%20all%20of%20a%20sudden.%20A%20screaming%20sea%20of%20people%20were%20slowly%20losing%20their%20voice%20and%20by%20the%20time%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20arrived%20at%20the%20stadium%2C%20India%20had%20lost%20the%20plot.%20What%20was%20made%20for%20each%20other%20was%20now%20coming%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Australians%20were%20stamping%20all%20over%20the%20Indians.%20The%20crowd%20was%20not%20there%20to%20watch%20a%20cricket%20match.%20They%20were%20there%20to%20celebrate%20India%E2%80%99s%20win%2C%20not%20to%20applaud%20the%20wonderful%20cricket%20the%20Australians%20were%20playing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20even%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20presence%20could%20lift%20their%20spirits%20as%20all%20along%20they%20had%20believed%20he%20was%20the%20talisman%20that%20would%20ensure%20India%E2%80%99s%20win.%20Their%20world%20had%20collapsed%2C%20their%20dreams%20broken%20to%20shreds.%20They%20must%20have%20felt%20cheated%2C%20refusing%20to%20appreciate%20a%20four%20hit%2C%20a%20six%20struck%2C%20a%20century%20made%20and%20a%20victory%20achieved%20against%20all%20odds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Australian%20captain%20had%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20match%20said%20that%20they%20would%20draw%20energy%20from%20silencing%20the%20crowd.%20The%20hush%20that%20descended%20on%20the%20stadium%20Sunday%20night%20even%20while%20Cummins%20lifted%20the%20trophy%20may%20have%20pleased%20the%20Australian%20captain%2C%20but%20it%20sure%20had%20diminished%20India%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700486980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20173049%2FF_UEPDVXgAAmcLH.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-cricket-world-cup-2023-final-pradeep-magazine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20crowd%20was%20not%20there%20to%20watch%20a%20cricket%20match.%20They%20were%20there%20to%20celebrate%20India%E2%80%99s%20win%2C%20not%20to%20applaud%20the%20wonderful%20cricket%20the%20Australians%20were%20playing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A405%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-cricket-world-cup-2023-final-pradeep-magazine%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Robotics%20Team%20Reaches%20Uttarakhand%20Tunnel%2C%20Pipe%20Installed%20To%20Supply%20Food%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20devised%20a%20five-option%20action%20plan%20that%20involve%20drilling%20from%20three%20sides%20to%20access%20the%20trapped%20workers.%C2%A0%20Five%20different%20agencies%20have%20been%20tasked%20with%20carrying%20out%20each%20operation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETwo%20tunnels%20will%20be%20drilled%20horizontally%20from%20the%20right%20and%20left%20sides%20of%20the%20main%20tunnel%2C%20while%20a%20vertical%20shaft%20will%20be%20drilled%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20tunnel.%20The%20workers%20have%20been%20trapped%20in%20a%20400-metre%20buffer%20zone%20of%20the%20unfinished%20main%20tunnel%20since%20November%2012.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20big%20challenge%20is%20finding%20space%20for%20the%20multiple%20drilling%20machines%20needed%20in%20the%20hilly%20terrain%20and%20the%20time-consuming%20job%20of%20building%20motorable%20roads%2C%20which%20has%20started.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECurrently%2C%20a%20single%20machine%20is%20operating%20in%20the%20area%2C%20clearing%20the%20way%20for%20a%20heavier%20machine.%20Workers%20are%20also%20building%20a%20ramp%20from%20the%20main%20tunnel's%20entrance%20to%20its%20roof%20to%20transport%20the%20heavier%20machine.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20morning%2C%20a%20wider%20pipe%20was%20brought%20and%20is%20currently%20being%20installed.%20This%20will%20allow%20rescuers%20to%20deliver%20a%20wider%20variety%20of%20food%20and%20medicine%20to%20the%20trapped%20people.%20Earlier%2C%20only%20dry%20fruits%20could%20be%20sent%20in.%20With%20the%20new%20pipe%2C%20the%20authorities%20will%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20more%20substantial%20meals.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EToday%2C%20an%20international%20tunnelling%20expert%20team%20arrived%20ta%20the%20spot.%20International%20Tunnelling%20and%20Underground%20Space%20Association%20president%20Arnold%20Dix%20is%20overseeing%20the%20operations.%20A%20robotics%20team%20from%20defence%20research%20organization%20DRDO%20has%20also%20reached.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%20the%20last%20week%2C%20several%20plans%20to%20cut%20through%20the%2040-meter%20rock%20wall%20fell%20through.%20It%20had%20also%20backfired%20twice%2C%20bringing%20down%20more%20rocks%20and%20rubble%20from%20the%20unplastered%20roof%2C%20extending%20the%20depth%20of%20the%20rock%20wall%20from%20around%2040%20to%20over%2070%20meters.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20last%20rock-fall%20took%20place%20on%20Friday%2C%20when%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20use%20an%20American%20Auger%20drill%20flown%20in%20from%20Delhi.%20The%20drill%20machine%20that%20was%20being%20used%20before%20that%2C%20had%20broken%20down%20and%20work%20had%20to%20be%20stopped%20till%20the%20new%20one%20reached.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInitially%20the%20plan%20was%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20rock%20wall%20and%20insert%20a%20pipe%20with%20a%20width%20of%20around%203%20feet%20through%20which%20the%20people%20could%20be%20evacuated.%20But%20after%20repeated%20rockfalls%2C%20the%20authorities%20decided%20on%20a%20radically%20different%20approach.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOn%20November%2012%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20the%204.5-km%20tunnel%20on%20the%20Brahmakhal-Yamunotri%20National%20Highway%20has%20collapsed%2C%20trapping%2041%20workers.%20The%20tunnel%20--%20meant%20to%20join%20Silkyara%20and%20Dandalgaon%20in%20Uttarkashi%20--%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Char%20Dham%20project.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700486940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fg09arft8_uttarakhand-tunnel-collapse_625x300_20_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-now-a-five-point-plan-to-rescue-men-trapped-in-uttarakhand-tunnel-4589820%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Unable%20to%20rescue%2041%20labourers%20trapped%20inside%20a%20tunnel%20for%20more%20than%20a%20week%2C%20the%20agencies%20involved%20in%20the%20operation%20are%20working%20on%20an%20alternative%20plan.%20This%20one%20involves%20tunnelling%20sideways%20and%20boring%20from%20the%20top%20to%20build%20a%20vertical%20shaft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-now-a-five-point-plan-to-rescue-men-trapped-in-uttarakhand-tunnel-4589820%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-now-a-five-point-plan-to-rescue-men-trapped-in-uttarakhand-tunnel-4589820%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-now-a-five-point-plan-to-rescue-men-trapped-in-uttarakhand-tunnel-4589820%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BParty%20Told%20Me%20To%20Move%20On%26quot%3B%3A%20Sachin%20Pilot%20On%20Feud%20With%20Ashok%20Gehlot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20ex-Rajasthan%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Sachin%20Pilot%20made%20headlines%20-%20for%20leading%20a%20rebellion%20that%20nearly%20brought%20down%20his%20party's%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3Cbr%3E%5CnFast-forward%20to%20today%20and%20an%20energetic%20Mr%20Pilot%20is%20on%20the%20frontlines%20of%20a%20re-election%20bid%2C%20fighting%20(in%20apparent%20lock-step)%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20long-time%20rival%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20to%20ensure%20the%20Congress%20trumps%20the%20BJP%20and%20retains%20power%20in%20a%20state%20that%20has%20not%20voted%20for%20an%20incumbent%20in%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20caught%20up%20with%20Sachin%20Pilot%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20-%20as%20he%20jumped%20in%20and%20out%20of%20helicopters%20-%20to%20discuss%20the%20November%2025th%20election%20and%20the%20Congress'%20game-plan%2C%20and%20his%20relationship%20with%20Mr%20Gehlot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDouble%20engine...%20double%20engine.%20What%20double%20engine%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pilot%20thundered%20at%20one%20rally%2C%20making%20pointed%20swipes%20at%20the%20BJP's%20promise%20of%20development%20for%20states%20that%20vote%20for%20the%20saffron%20party%20in%20both%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20engine%20failed%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh...%20another%20in%20Karnataka.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20confident%20of%20a%20positive%20result%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20a%20NDTV%20pre-poll%20survey%20last%20month%20suggests%20they%20have%20cause%20for%20optimism%3B%2076%20per%20cent%20of%20voters%20seem%20satisfied%20with%20its%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Congress'%20Chances%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20party%20is%20energised.%20We%20have%20never%20won%20back-to-back%20Rajasthan%20elections.%20Our%20attempt%20now%20is%20to%20break%20this%20cycle%20of%20a%20revolving%20door%20(and)%20we%20are%20well-placed%20to%20do%20that.%20There%20is%20a%20change%20of%20mood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20is%20delivery%20of%20social%20welfare%20schemes.%20If%20people%20don't%20feel%20you%20are%20credible...%20they%20won't%20believe%20in%20you.%20In%20Karnataka%20we%20delivered%20immediately...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%2C%20underlining%20the%20Congress'%20game-plan%20-%20to%20bank%20on%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government's%20welfare%20schemes%20to%20pull%20in%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20at%20social%20welfare%20and%20also%20investment%20and%20wealth%20creation%20(for%20the%20people%20of%20Rajasthan).%20We%20need%20an%20equitable%20Rajasthan...%20we%20need%20to%20give%20youth%20opportunities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Chief%20Ministerial%20Race%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20amid%20speculation%20Mr%20Pilot%20could%20finally%20be%20named%20Chief%20Minister%20(should%20the%20Congress%20win%20this%20election)%2C%20the%20NDTV%20pre-poll%20survey%20also%20indicated%20less%20than%2010%20per%20cent%20want%20him%20in%20that%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstandably%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20was%20keen%20to%20play%20down%20any%20such%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Congress%2C%20whenever%20party%20(central)%20leadership%20takes%20a%20call%20then%20that%20is%20final%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20long-standing%20tradition%20(that)%20we%20don't%20declare%20a%20CM%20face.%20We%20are%20a%20national%20party%20and%20we%20don't%20have%20just%20one%20face.%20Once%20we%20get%20the%20mandate%2C%20then%20it%20is%20up%20to%20the%20MLAs%20to%20decide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Feud%20With%20Ashok%20Gehlot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20in%20the%20past...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20the%20big%20question.%20%26quot%3BWe%20met%20(Congress%20boss%20Mallikarjun)%20Kharge%20and%20(Rahul)%20Gandhi...%20the%20party%20took%20cognisance%20(of%20my%20concerns)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20party%20high%20command%20told%20me%20to%20forgive%20and%20forget%2C%20and%20move%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20too%2C%20Sachin%20Pilot%20had%20offered%20to%20%26quot%3Bforgive%20and%20forget%26quot%3B%20the%20free-for-all%20exchange%20of%20barbs%20Mr%20Gehlot%20and%20he%20had%20exchanged.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20a%20little%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20then%20it%20is%20not%20a%20big%20issue%20because%20the%20party%20and%20the%20public%20are%20more%20important%20than%20any%20individual%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20focus%20now%20is%20to%20work%20together...%20there%20is%20no%20personal%20animosity.%20We%20haven't%20won%20consecutive%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%20for%2030%20years.%20Why%3F%20We%20need%20to%20introspect%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Exam%20Paper%20Leaks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pilot%20also%20spoke%20on%20exam%20paper%20leaks%20in%20Rajasthan%20-%20which%20made%20headlines%20last%20month%20after%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20searched%20the%20home%20of%20the%20Congress'%20state%20chief%2C%20Govind%20Dotasara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20welcome%20every%20step%20to%20curb%20this%20menace...%20Rajasthan%20has%20made%20a%20law%20that%20(those%20who%20leak)%20papers%20will%20get%20life%20term...%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20before%20he%20switched%20tack%20to%20slam%20the%20BJP%20for%20%26quot%3Bunleashing%20the%20ED...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaks%20had%20triggered%20a%20temporary%20scare%20for%20the%20Congress%20after%20Sachin%20Pilot%20seemed%20to%20criticise%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20in%20public%2C%20raising%20fear%20of%20another%20bitter%20civil%20war%2C%20this%20time%20months%20before%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20will%20vote%20for%20a%20new%20government%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%20Saturday%2C%20with%20results%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700486880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fnfrcolbg_sachin-pilot-ndtv_625x300_20_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsachin-pilot-exclusive-interview-sachin-pilot-mocks-bjp-says-one-engine-failed-in-himachal-another-in-karnataka-4589941%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20years%20ago%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20ex-Rajasthan%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Sachin%20Pilot%20made%20headlines%20-%20for%20leading%20a%20rebellion%20that%20nearly%20brought%20down%20his%20party's%20government%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsachin-pilot-exclusive-interview-sachin-pilot-mocks-bjp-says-one-engine-failed-in-himachal-another-in-karnataka-4589941%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.amp