20alleging%20that%20the%20police%20had%20fabricated%20witness%20statements%20to%20arrest%20a%20local%20Muslim%20cleric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20faces%20three%20charges%20under%20the%20penal%20code%2C%20including%20criminal%20intimidation%2C%20intent%20to%20commit%20a%20criminal%20act%2C%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20and%20one%20count%20under%20UAPA%20pertaining%20to%20threatening%20witnesses.%C2%A0As%20of%20June%202023%2C%20Shahina%20is%20out%20on%20bail%20pending%20trial.%20If%20convicted%2C%20she%20faces%20a%20maximum%20of%20three%20years%20in%20prison%20and%20a%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Muslim%20by%20birth%2C%20Shahina%20has%20also%20been%20subjected%20to%20extensive%20harassment%20by%20Indian%20right-wing%20groups%20seeking%20to%20silence%20her%20reporting%20on%20religious%20minorities%20and%20vulnerable%20caste%20groups.%20She%20has%20faced%20persistent%20online%20harassment%20and%20lewd%20threats%2C%20and%20in%202020%2C%20several%20right-wing%20publications%20falsely%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fkerala-scribe-take-legal-action-after-right-wing-paper-falsely-calls-her-blast-accused%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimplicated%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0her%20in%20that%20Bengaluru%20bombing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20in%20Kochi%2C%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Shahina%20has%20worked%20as%20a%20reporter%2C%20production%20associate%2C%20and%20news%20anchor%20with%20well-known%20news%20outlets%20including%20Asianet%20News%2C%20Janayugom%2C%20Open%2C%20and%20The%20Federal.%20She%20also%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fasia_pacific%2Fshe-made-history-by-entering-a-holy-indian-shrine-her-family-locked-her-out-of-the-house%2F2019%2F02%2F10%2F7a0ed552-27d3-11e9-906e-9d55b6451eb4_story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtributed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Faggressive-testing-contact-tracing-cooked-meals-how-the-indian-state-of-kerala-flattened-its-coronavirus-curve%2F2020%2F04%2F10%2F3352e470-783e-11ea-a311-adb1344719a9_story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3EThe%20Washington%20Post.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPJ%20has%20said%20in%20its%20note%20announcing%20Shahina%E2%80%99s%20win%20that%20this%20also%20highlights%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20increasingly%20repressive%20environment%20for%20press%20freedom%2C%20with%20the%20targeting%20of%20journalists%20under%20draconian%20security%20laws%2C%20and%20toxic%20online%20campaigns%20particularly%20aimed%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpj.org%2F2022%2F01%2Fwomen-journalists-india-auction-apps-online-abuse%2F%5C%22%3Evilifying%3C%2Fa%3E%20women%20journalists%20and%20ethnic%20or%20religious%20minorities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20awardees%20for%20this%20year%20include%20Nika%20Gvaramia%20from%20Georgia%20(founder%20and%20director%20of%20independent%20broadcaster%2C%20Mtavari%20Arkhi)%2C%20Mar%C3%ADa%20Teresa%20Monta%C3%B1o%20from%20Mexico%20(investigative%20reporter%20and%20founder%20and%20editor%20of%20The%20Observer%2C%20a%20fact-checking%20and%20investigative%20website)%20and%20Ferdinand%20Ayit%C3%A9%20from%20Togo%20(head%20of%20L%E2%80%99Alternative%2C%20one%20of%20Togo%E2%80%99s%20top%20investigative%20outlets).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%E2%80%99s%20Gwen%20Ifill%20Press%20Freedom%20Award%20from%20CPJ%2C%20which%20goes%20to%20%E2%80%9Can%20individual%20who%20has%20shown%20extraordinary%20and%20sustained%20achievement%20in%20the%20cause%20of%20press%20freedom%E2%80%9D%2C%20has%20been%20awarded%20to%20Alberto%20Ibarg%C3%BCen%2C%20who%20recently%20announced%20he%20is%20stepping%20down%20as%20president%20of%20the%20Knight%20Foundation%20after%2018%20years%20at%20its%20helm.%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20his%20leadership%2C%20the%20foundation%20invested%20over%20%242.3%20billion%20in%20journalism%2C%20arts%2C%20economic%20development%2C%20and%20research.%20Ibarg%C3%BCen%20is%20the%20former%20publisher%20of%20the%20Miami%20Herald%20and%20El%20Nuevo%20Herald.%20During%20his%20tenure%2C%20the%20Miami%20Herald%20won%20three%20Pulitzer%20Prizes%20and%20El%20Nuevo%20Herald%20won%20Spain%E2%80%99s%20Ortega%20y%20Gasset%20Prize%20for%20excellence%20in%20journalism.%20He%20served%20on%20the%20board%20of%20CPJ%20from%201993%20to%202005%2C%E2%80%9D%20CPJ%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700483609000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20180232%2F1680487852886-01-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Findian-journalist-k-k-shahina-among-winners-of-cpjs-international-press-freedom-awards%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shahina%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20journalists%20to%20be%20charged%20under%20the%20draconian%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20for%20her%20work%20in%20Tehelka%20magazine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Findian-journalist-k-k-shahina-among-winners-of-cpjs-international-press-freedom-awards%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Singer%20hurt%20'while%20restraining%20backstage%20intruder'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700483100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F70x70%2Fskynews-kyuhyun-k-pop-super-junior_6366530.jpg%3F20231120122312%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fk-pop-star-kyuhyun-injured-while-restraining-knife-wielding-intruder-at-seoul-theatre-record-label-says-13012222%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22K-pop%20star%20Kyuhyun%20has%20been%20injured%20while%20attempting%20to%20restrain%20an%20%26quot%3Bintruder%26quot%3B%20carrying%20a%20knife%20inside%20a%20theatre%2C%20his%20record%20label%20has%20