into%20the%20bombardment%20of%20Palestinian%20life%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20possibilities%20of%20a%20ceasefire.%20%E2%80%9CNone%2C%20no%20possibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20deadpanned.%20A%20pause%20could%20perhaps%20be%20mandated%2C%20but%20only%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20the%20captives%20taken%20by%20Palestinian%20militants%20in%20their%20audacious%20October%207%20raid%20into%20southern%20settlements%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20an%20active%20patron%20of%20two%20wars%20in%20distinct%20theatres%20%E2%80%93%20aside%20from%20low-level%20conflicts%20across%20the%20globe%20the%20US%20plays%20sides%20in%20%E2%80%93%20Biden%20is%20unabashed%20about%20his%20double%20standards.%20His%20special%20assistant%20in%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%2C%20John%20Kirby%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D32JQILY2jVg%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20weepy%20and%20maudlin%20on%20live%20TV%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20when%20speaking%20of%20civilian%20suffering%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20as%20also%20the%20casualties%20Israel%20suffered%20on%20October%207.%20About%20civilian%20casualties%20among%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20he%20was%20brusque%20and%20business-like.%20The%20US%20would%20lay%20down%20no%20%E2%80%9Cred%20lines%E2%80%9D%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20operations%2C%20Kirby%20said%2C%20a%20response%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstuff%20happens%E2%80%9D%20comment%20from%20US%20defence%20secretary%20Donald%20Rumsfeld%20(as%20he%20then%20was)%20after%20the%20invasion%20of%20Iraq%20in%202003%20and%20that%20country%E2%80%99s%20descent%20into%20blood%20mayhem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBiden%20visited%20Israel%20ten%20days%20into%20the%20conflict.%20The%20Al%20Ahli%20Baptist%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%20had%20just%20been%20bombed%2C%20and%20his%20response%20was%20a%20sporting%20metaphor%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJBNdf2p1mU0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cbased%20on%20what%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%2C%20the%20other%20team%20must%20have%20done%20it%2C%20not%20you%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20he%20said%20sitting%20across%20from%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20far-right%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%20Dissembling%20was%20the%20theme%20after%20his%20return%20home%2C%20when%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fdespite-bidens-doubts-humanitarian-agencies-consider-gaza-toll-reliable-2023-10-27%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebrushed%20off%20the%20toll%20of%20deaths%20and%20injuries%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20put%20out%20by%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20health%20ministry%20as%20implausible%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBiden%20emboldened%20further%20outrages.%20In%20the%20days%20that%20followed%2C%20Israel%20attacked%20every%20healthcare%20facility%20in%20Gaza%2C%20ambulance%20convoys%2C%20schools%2C%20mosques%20and%20churches%2C%20with%20lethal%20force.%20The%20repeated%20bombardment%20of%20refugee%20camps%20under%20the%20UN%20administration%20was%20called%20out%20as%20a%20war%20crime%2C%20but%20this%20unequivocal%20finding%20by%20observers%20on%20the%20ground%20gained%20no%20official%20endorsement%20from%20global%20watchdog%20bodies%20such%20as%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20or%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2013%2C%20the%20Israeli%20army%E2%80%99s%20spokesman%20took%20embedded%20reporters%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20bombed-out%20shell%20of%20the%20Rantisi%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza.%20He%20pointed%20to%20a%20chalkboard%20written%20in%20Arabic%2C%20alleging%20it%20was%20a%20duty%20roster%20for%20the%20militant%20resistance%20organisation%20Hamas.%20The%20claim%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jordannews.jo%2FSection-20%2FMiddle-East%2FIsraeli-army-s-hospital-claim-in-Gaza-debunked-32311%5C%22%3Edebunked%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20first%20glance%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20chalkboard%20did%20nothing%20more%20sinister%20than%20list%20the%20days%20of%20the%20week%20in%20the%20Arabic%20script%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20following%20day%2C%20when%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20invasion%20force%20stepped%20up%20the%20ferocity%20of%20its%20attack%20on%20the%20Al-Shifa%20Hospital%2C%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20largest%20health%20facility%20and%20the%20last%20to%20retain%20a%20level%20of%20serviceability%2C%20it%20claimed%20to%20be%20carrying%20out%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprecise%20and%20targeted%E2%80%9D%20operation%20against%20armed%20Hamas%20fighters%20sheltering%20behind%20the%20protection%20afforded%20by%20the%20hospital.%20The%20US%20asserted%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fwhite-house-says-it-has-evidence-hamas-using-al-shifa-hospital-run-military-2023-11-14%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%20had%20evidence%20proving%20the%20Israeli%20case%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20No%20third%20party%20stepped%20up%20to%20endorse%20the%20claim%2C%20neither%20was%20any%20allowed%20in%20to%20verify.%20The%20Israeli%20onslaught%20went%20on%20regardless.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20would%20be%20the%20obligations%20of%20global%20watchdog%20bodies%2C%20which%20have%20shown%20great%20alacrity%20in%20bringing%20indictments%20against%20soft%20targets%3F%20There%20is%20a%20framework%20of%20legal%20obligations%20global%20players%20are%20expected%20to%20honour%2C%20a%20crystallisation%20of%20the%20learning%20experiences%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccivilised%20West%E2%80%9D%20after%20it%20dragged%20the%20world%20through%20two%20rounds%20of%20industrial-scale%20bloodshed%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century.%20These%20were%20embedded%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icrc.org%2Fen%2Fwar-and-law%2Ftreaties-customary-law%2Fgeneva-conventions%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGeneva%20Conventions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20related%20global%20covenants.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fgenocideprevention%2Fdocuments%2Fatrocity-crimes%2FDoc.33_GC-IV-EN.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efourth%20of%20the%20Geneva%20Conventions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(GCIV)%20and%20the%20First%20Additional%20Protocol%20are%20of%20particular%20relevance%2C%20since%20they%20deal%20with%20the%20protection%20of%20civilians%20in%20armed%20conflict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F12125115%2Fimage1170x530cropped-4.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F12125115%2Fimage1170x530cropped-4.jpg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F12125115%2Fimage1170x530cropped-4-300x136.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F12125115%2Fimage1170x530cropped-4-1024x464.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684525%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAl%20Shifa%20hospital%20is%20being%20used%20as%20shelter%20for%20displaced%20families%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20WHO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20rules%20applicable%20in%20all%20forms%20of%20conflict%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20status%20of%20belligerents%20as%20state%20or%20non-state%20actors%2C%20is%20Article%2033%20of%20the%20GCIV%2C%20which%20prohibits%20%E2%80%9Ccollective%20penalties%20and%20likewise%20all%20measures%20of%20intimidation%20or%20terrorism%E2%80%9D.%20This%20is%20followed%20by%20an%20entire%20section%20on%20%E2%80%9COccupied%20Territories%E2%80%9D%20with%20no%20fewer%20than%20fifteen%20articles.%20Among%20these%20is%20one%20(Article%2055)%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20Occupying%20Power%20to%20ensure%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20food%20and%20medical%20supplies%20of%20the%20population%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20in%20particular%2C%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbring%20in%20the%20necessary%20foodstuffs%2C%20medical%20stores%20and%20other%20articles%20if%20the%20resources%20of%20the%20occupied%20territory%20are%20inadequate%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImmediately%20afterwards%20is%20the%20stipulation%20(Article%2056)%2C%20that%20the%20maintenance%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmedical%20and%20hospital%20establishments%20and%20services%2C%20public%20health%20and%20hygiene%20in%20the%20occupied%20territory%E2%80%9D%20is%20an%20obligation%20of%20the%20Occupying%20Power%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20the%20co-operation%20of%20national%20and%20local%20authorities%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%20has%20in%20the%20past%2C%20argued%20that%20it%20is%20not%20bound%20by%20the%20Geneva%20Conventions%20in%20any%20of%20the%20occupied%20territories%20because%20there%20was%20no%20sovereign%20power%20supplanted%20by%20its%20military%20conquest.%20Military%20lines%20of%20control%20were%20drawn%20at%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20in%201948%2C%20after%20hostilities%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20Egyptian%20and%20Jordanian%20armies%20ended.%20Israel%20merely%20replaced%20one%20form%20of%20military%20administration%20with%20another%20in%201967%2C%20when%20it%20rolled%20into%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20after%20blitzing%20the%20Arab%20armies%20in%20the%20Six-Day%20War.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20perspective%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Freports%2F2001%2Fisrael%2Fhebron6-04.htm%23P308_51771%5C%22%3Erejected%20by%20every%20expert%3C%2Fa%3E%20body%20since%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0the%20language%20of%20the%20Geneva%20Conventions%20creates%20no%20such%20distinction.%20Its%20protections%20rather%2C%20are%20extended%20to%20all%20persons%20who%20%E2%80%9Cat%20a%20given%20moment%20and%20in%20any%20manner%20whatsoever%2C%20find%20themselves%2C%20in%20case%20of%20a%20conflict%20or%20occupation%2C%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20Party%20to%20the%20conflict%20or%20Occupying%20Power%20of%20which%20they%20are%20not%20nationals%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%20has%20since%20added%20another%20element%20to%20its%20ideological%20armament%2C%20with%20the%20claim%20that%20after%20its%20withdrawal%20of%20all%20military%20deployments%20and%20settlements%20in%202004%2C%20the%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20ceased%20to%20be%20one%20of%20occupation%2C%20since%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20%E2%80%9Ceffective%20control%E2%80%9D.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20Israel%20has%20absolute%20control%20over%20all%20routes%20of%20access%20to%20the%20strip%20through%20air%2C%20land%20and%20sea%2C%20has%20maintained%20a%20powerful%20military%20presence%20at%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20border%20with%20Egypt%2C%20and%20repeatedly%20intervened%20by%20military%20means%2C%20massively%20and%20at%20times%20of%20its%20choosing.%20In%202007%2C%20it%20fomented%20a%20series%20of%20pitched%20battles%20between%20Hamas%20and%20the%20rival%20resistance%20group%20Fatah%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20overturn%20the%20result%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20National%20Council%20election%20of%202006%2C%20which%20the%20former%20had%20won.%20Effectively%20splitting%20the%20two%20and%20confining%20Hamas%20to%20Gaza%2C%20Israel%20ratcheted%20up%20the%20severity%20of%20its%20blockade%20of%20the%20territory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%20justifies%20the%20blockade%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20is%20engaged%20in%20an%20armed%20conflict%20with%20Hamas.%20In%202010%2C%20when%20a%20Turkish%20ship%20bringing%20essential%20food%20and%20medicines%20approached%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20shores%2C%20it%20was%20interdicted%20by%20an%20Israeli%20naval%20task%20force.%20Commandos%20forcibly%20boarded%20the%20ship%20and%20killed%20nine%20peace%20volunteers%2C%20claiming%20the%20alibi%20that%20they%20met%20with%20violent%20resistance.%20Israel%20argued%20before%20a%20formal%20inquest%20that%20it%20was%20in%20a%20state%20of%20war%20with%20Gaza%20which%20made%20its%20blockade%20legal%20and%20its%20interdiction%20of%20the%20Turkish%20ship%20a%20permitted%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20GCIV%20stipulates%20that%20warring%20parties%20will%20not%20use%20deprivation%20of%20the%20basic%20necessities%20of%20civilian%20life%20as%20a%20weapon%20of%20war.%20Article%2023%20requires%20all%20contracting%20parties%20to%20%E2%80%9Callow%20the%20free%20passage%20of%20all%20consignments%20of%20medical%20and%20hospital%20stores%2C%20%E2%80%A6%20essential%20foodstuffs%2C%20clothing%20and%20tonics%20intended%20for%20children%20under%20fifteen%2C%20expectant%20mothers%20and%20maternity%20cases%E2%80%9D.%20Article%2070%20of%20the%20First%20Additional%20Protocol%20requires%20that%20in%20the%20event%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20civilian%20population%20of%20any%20territory%20under%20the%20control%20of%20a%20Party%20to%20the%20conflict%2C%20other%20than%20occupied%20territory%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20not%20adequately%20provided%20%E2%80%A6.%20relief%20actions%20which%20are%20humanitarian%20and%20impartial%20in%20character%20and%20conducted%20without%20any%20adverse%20distinction%20shall%20be%20undertaken%2C%20subject%20to%20the%20agreement%20of%20the%20Parties%20concerned%20in%20such%20relief%20actions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%20is%20in%20clear%20and%20material%20breach%20of%20these%20stipulations%2C%20even%20in%20a%20declared%20state%20of%20war%2C%20and%20even%20if%20its%20denial%20of%20the%20status%20of%20an%20Occupying%20Power%20were%20to%20be%20accepted.%20This%20has%20never%20been%20a%20secret%20from%20the%20global%20community.%20The%20purpose%20of%20the%20blockade%20was%20put%20with%20absolute%20clarity%20by%20an%20adviser%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%20in%202009%3A%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cto%20put%20the%20Palestinians%20on%20a%20diet%2C%20but%20not%20to%20make%20them%20die%20of%20hunger%E2%80%9D.%20Israel%20also%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20blockade%20on%20Gaza%20is%20a%20form%20of%20legitimate%20%E2%80%9Ceconomic%20warfare%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20official%20document%20noted%20in%202010%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20blockade%20of%20Gaza%20conformed%20with%20the%20principle%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20country%20has%20the%20right%20to%20decide%20that%20it%20chooses%20not%20to%20engage%20in%20economic%20relations%20or%20to%20give%20economic%20assistance%20to%20the%20other%20party%20to%20the%20conflict%2C%20or%20that%20it%20wishes%20to%20operate%20using%20%E2%80%98economic%20warfare%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fbook%2F10.1007%2F978-90-6704-811-8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EYearbook%20of%20International%20Humanitarian%20Law%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%202010%3A%20402-03).%20In%202011%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncronline.org%2Fblogs%2Fncr-today%2Fwikileaks-israel-wanted-keep-gaza-economy-brink-collapse%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20cable%20unearthed%20by%20Wikileaks%20has%20Israel%20informing%20the%20US%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20its%20object%20was%20to%20keep%20the%20%E2%80%9CGaza%20economy%20functioning%20at%20the%20lowest%20level%20possible%20consistent%20with%20avoiding%20a%20humanitarian%20crisis%E2%80%9D.%20To%20achieve%20this%20goal%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmondoweiss.net%2F2010%2F10%2Fisraeli-formula-maintains-a-minimum-of-breathing-space-in-gaza%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIsraeli%20officials%20employed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Cmathematical%20formulas%20to%20monitor%20foodstuffs%20and%20other%20basic%20goods%20entering%20the%20Strip%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20amount%20of%20supplies%20entering%20was%20neither%20less%20nor%20more%20than%20the%20(permitted)%20amount%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20privations%20are%20imposed%20on%20Gaza%20with%20the%20object%20of%20creating%20unbearable%20stresses%20in%20society.%20With%20a%20sufficient%20accumulation%20of%20such%20stresses%2C%20Israel%20believes%2C%20Gaza%20would%20be%20compelled%20to%20evict%20Hamas%20from%20all%20positions%20of%20authority.%20This%20puts%20Israel%20flagrantly%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20law%20of%20armed%20conflict%2C%20since%20the%20enforced%20suffering%20of%20civilians%20cannot%20be%20used%20as%20a%20means%20of%20achieving%20political%20and%20military%20objectives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerversely%2C%20the%20larger%20political%20context%20creates%20an%20incentive%20for%20Israel%20to%20sustain%20the%20blockade%20indefinitely%2C%20irrespective%20of%20any%20expression%20of%20peaceable%20intentions%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20Gaza%20has%20long%20since%20been%20banished%20from%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20ambitions.%20It%20is%20seen%20as%20unmanageable%2C%20just%20too%20minute%20a%20territory%20with%20many%20more%20people%20than%20Israel%20can%20deal%20with.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20aims%20today%20include%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20the%20annexation%20of%20a%20substantial%20part%20of%20the%20West%20Bank.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fopinion%2Finternational%2F4268794-the-symbiotic-relationship-between-netanyahu-and-hamas%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKeeping%20Gaza%20in%20in%20a%20permanent%20state%20of%20global%20ostracism%20and%20blockade%2C%20serves%20its%20purposes%20very%20well%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Israel%20was%20already%20in%20a%20declared%20state%20of%20war%20with%20Gaza%20till%20the%20morning%20of%20October%207%2C%20the%20events%20that%20day%20were%20obviously%20part%20of%20a%20continuum.%20UN%20secretary%20general%20Antonio%20Guterres%20did%20no%20more%20than%20point%20this%20out%2C%20when%20he%20set%20off%20a%20frisson%20of%20faux%20outrage%20from%20the%20Israeli%20ambassador%20to%20the%20world%20body%2C%20who%20called%20on%20him%20to%20resign%20and%20announced%20that%20all%20cooperation%20with%20its%20agencies%20would%20cease.%20That%20is%20yet%20another%20instance%2C%20one%20among%20an%20infinite%20number%2C%20when%20Israel%20has%20used%20bluster%20and%20bullying%2C%20with%20the%20connivance%20of%20the%20US%2C%20to%20force%20certain%20themes%20off%20the%20global%20dialogue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20the%20demonstrators%20who%20refuse%20to%20vacate%20the%20streets%20bear%20testimony%20to%20the%20manifest%20failure%20of%20this%20strategy%2C%20certain%20curiosities%20endure.%20If%20Israel%20was%20already%20in%20a%20war%20with%20Gaza%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F08%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-gaza-attack-hostages-response-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhy%20was%20the%20declaration%20or%20the%20renewal%20of%20such%20a%20state%20on%20October%207%20necessary%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%20And%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20war%20that%20was%20already%20underway%2C%20how%20were%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20actions%20of%20October%207%20to%20be%20viewed%3F%20To%20add%20to%20these%20curiosities%2C%20Israel%20that%20day%20sought%20in%20a%20noisy%2C%20obstreperous%20clamour%20of%20self-righteousness%2C%20the%20right%20to%20defend%20itself%20against%20a%20people%20it%20had%20placed%20on%20a%20blockade%20and%20kept%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20starvation%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20policy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30145614%2FScreenshot-2023-10-30-at-2.56.00%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30145614%2FScreenshot-2023-10-30-at-2.56.00%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30145614%2FScreenshot-2023-10-30-at-2.56.00%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x164.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30145614%2FScreenshot-2023-10-30-at-2.56.00%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x561.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682491%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22657%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMembers%20of%20the%20orthodox%20Hasidic%20Jewish%20community%20lead%20the%20call%20for%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Brooklyn%2C%20NY%2C%20Saturday%2C%20October%2029.%20Photo%3A%20Sunita%20Viswanath%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20term%20%E2%80%9Cterrorism%E2%80%9D%20applied%20to%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20has%20empowered%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20grossly%20disproportionate%20response%20under%20a%20dangerously%20vague%20and%20open-ended%20mission%20of%20%E2%80%9Celiminating%E2%80%9D%20Hamas%20for%20all%20time.%20The%20First%20Additional%20Protocol%20by%20Article%201(4)%2C%20extends%20all%20the%20protections%20of%20the%20Geneva%20Conventions%20to%20peoples%20%E2%80%9Cfighting%20against%20colonial%20domination%20and%20alien%20occupation%20and%20against%20racist%20regimes%20in%20the%20exercise%20of%20their%20right%20of%20self-determination%E2%80%9D.%20This%20has%20been%20read%2C%20though%20not%20without%20controversy%2C%20as%20the%20legally%20enshrined%20right%20of%20an%20occupied%20people%20to%20assert%20their%20right%20to%20self-determination%20by%20armed%20means.%20Armed%20resistance%20is%20legitimate%20where%20necessary%2C%20though%20within%20the%20universally%20applicable%20norms%20of%20proportionality%20and%20military%20necessity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CProportionality%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20difficult%20parameter%20to%20estimate%20in%20all%20circumstances.%20But%20when%20weighed%20in%20the%20scale%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20history%20of%20occupation%20and%20blockade%2C%20and%20the%20massive%20military%20operations%20it%20has%20carried%20out%20in%20Gaza%20prior%20to%20October%207%2C%20it%20becomes%20virtually%20impossible%20to%20quantify.%20Leaving%20that%20aside%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fact%20that%20video%20records%20from%20that%20day%2C%20reviewed%20by%20respected%20global%20rights%20bodies%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F18%2Fisrael%2Fpalestine-videos-hamas-led-attacks-verified%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehave%20provided%20undeniable%20evidence%20of%20war%20crimes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20warranting%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProportionality%20in%20the%20application%20of%20international%20legal%20norms%20would%20then%20require%20an%20investigation%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20conduct%2C%20both%20before%20and%20after%20October%207.%20And%20Israel%20has%20very%20early%20on%2C%20signalled%20its%20utter%20disdain%20of%20every%20norm%2C%20with%20its%20deliberate%20policy%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Flatest%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2Fdamning-evidence-of-war-crimes-as-israeli-attacks-wipe-out-entire-families-in-gaza%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebombing%20entire%20neighbourhoods%20out%20of%20existence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20its%20order%20for%20the%20relocation%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20residents%2C%20and%20its%20attacks%20on%20hospitals%20after%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F14-10-2023-evacuation-orders-by-israel-to-hospitals-in-northern-gaza-are-a-death-sentence-for-the-sick-and-injured%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eserving%20brief%20notice%20for%20their%20evacuation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20the%20very%20visible%20evidence%20of%20mass%20murder%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20call%20for%20the%20nuclear%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20by%20an%20Israeli%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20Amihai%20Eliyahu.%20He%20earned%20a%20reprimand%20from%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fnov%2F05%2Fnetanyahu-reprimands-israeli-minister-over-gaza-nuclear-option-comment%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eperhaps%20more%20for%20the%20public%20revelation%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20clandestine%20nuclear%20arsenal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20than%20for%20the%20genocidal%20intent.%20Avi%20Dichter%2C%20another%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20spoke%20of%20the%20ongoing%20operations%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CGaza%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enakba%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20or%20catastrophe%2C%20an%20Arabic%20term%20used%20to%20describe%20the%20mass%20displacement%20of%20Palestinians%20that%20accompanied%20the%20creation%20of%20Israel%20in%201948.%20When%20questioned%20about%20this%20assertion%2C%20Mark%20Regev%2C%20an%20adviser%20to%20the%20Israeli%20prime%20minister%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHD-yRuTasHU%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eembraced%20the%20sentiment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20ascribing%20all%20the%20blame%2C%20as%20he%20put%20it%2C%20to%20irresponsible%20Palestinian%20leadership.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20number%20of%20special%20rapporteurs%20and%20independent%20experts%20retained%20by%20the%20UN%20for%20their%20special%20expertise%20have%20meanwhile%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fpress-releases%2F2023%2F11%2Fgaza-un-experts-call-international-community-prevent-genocide-against%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CThe%2520international%2520community%2520has%2520an%2CUN%2520system%2520as%2520a%2520whole.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewarned%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20words%20and%20deeds%20express%20an%20overt%20genocidal%20intent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20deeply%20disturbed%20by%20the%20failure%20of%20governments%20to%20heed%20our%20call%20and%20to%20achieve%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire.%20We%20are%20also%20profoundly%20concerned%20about%20the%20support%20of%20certain%20governments%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20of%20warfare%20against%20the%20besieged%20population%20of%20Gaza%2C%20and%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20international%20system%20to%20mobilise%20to%20prevent%20genocide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20call%20to%20action%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20international%20community%2C%20including%20not%20only%20States%20but%20also%20non-State%20actors%20such%20as%20businesses%2C%20must%20do%20everything%20it%20can%20to%20immediately%20end%20the%20risk%20of%20genocide%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20and%20ultimately%20end%20Israeli%20apartheid%20and%20occupation%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20territory.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInternational%20law%20is%20of%20course%20an%20imperfect%20instrument%20to%20enforce%20the%20will%20of%20the%20global%20community.%20With%20all%20its%20ambiguities%2C%20the%20Geneva%20Conventions%20are%20the%20best%20available%20guide%20to%20how%20the%20world%20should%20be%2C%20not%20to%20how%20the%20world%20is.%20In%20reality%2C%20the%20law%20is%20what%20the%20powerful%20say%20it%20is.%20An%20ancient%20adage%20resurfaced%20by%20the%20historian%20E.H.%20Carr%20in%20his%20classic%20critique%20of%20the%20theory%20of%20international%20relations%20puts%20it%20best%3A%20justice%20is%20the%20right%20of%20the%20strong.%20Now%2C%20more%20than%20ever%2C%20is%20a%20time%20when%20international%20civil%20society%20has%20to%20agitate%20for%20the%20right%20to%20be%20heard%20by%20ruling%20establishments.%20Global%20demonstrations%20demanding%20that%20Israel%20be%20held%20accountable%20have%20not%20shown%20any%20sign%20of%20fatigue%2C%20despite%20the%20forces%20arrayed%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20and%20the%20application%20of%20draconian%20new%20laws%20to%20silence%20their%20voices.%20That%20is%20perhaps%20the%20sole%20bright%20spot%20in%20a%20bleak%20global%20scenario.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fsukumar-muralidharan%5C%22%3ESukumar%20Muralidharan%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20independent%20writer%20and%20researcher%20based%20in%20the%20Delhi%20region.%20He%20has%20worked%20in%20print%20media%2C%20as%20a%20journalism%20instructor%20and%20trainer%2C%20and%20press%20freedom%20campaigner.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700481646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16120732%2Fimage1170x530cropped-5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgaza-urgency-war-crime-prosecutions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20writes%20its%20own%20rules%20to%20suit%20its%20purposes%2C%20but%20global%20civil%20society%20needs%20to%20sustain%20the%20pressure%20till%20war%20crimes%20investigations%20lead%20to%20prosecutions%20for%20the%20mass%20murder%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgaza-urgency-war-crime-prosecutions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20The%20Who%E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Yadav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20164736%2FScreenshot-2023-11-20-at-4.41.07.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Yadav%20(18%2C650%2C119%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20mention%20of%20castes%20is%20found%20in%20written%20records%20up%20until%20what%20is%20known%20as%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20civilisation.%20Besides%20farmers%20and%20craftsmen%2C%20there%20were%20ruling%20classes%20but%20no%20castes.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20castes%20even%20in%20the%20Ajivika%20traditions%20of%20Bihar.%20What%20one%20does%20find%20is%20only%20a%20classification%20based%20on%20occupational%20identity.%20For%20example%2C%20Makkhali%20Gosala%20was%20a%20shepherd%20brought%20up%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETeli%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20family.%20Makkhali%20Gosala%20was%20the%20originator%20of%20Niyativad%20or%20fatalism%2C%20who%20rejected%20the%20concept%20of%20god%20and%20propounded%20that%20there%20is%20destiny%20behind%20every%20event%20that%20happens%20in%20the%20world%20and%20there%20is%20no%20controller.%20This%20ideology%20of%20Gosala%20was%20carried%20forward%20by%20Mahavir%20and%20Buddha%2C%20who%20laid%20down%20the%20principles%20of%20eternalism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20467px)%2085vw%2C%20467px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22467%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20talk%20about%20Bihar%2C%20we%20are%20referring%20to%20that%20region%20which%20helped%20shape%20the%20ideology%20of%20this%20country%20at%20whose%20core%20was%20community%20and%20not%20caste.%20For%20example%2C%20Buddha%E2%80%99s%20teachings%20stood%20in%20opposition%20to%20Brahminism.%20While%20the%20religion%20of%20Brahmins%20had%20many%20restrictions%20for%20Shudras%20and%20promoted%20untouchability%2C%20Buddhism%20preached%20respect%20and%20equal%20rights%20for%20all.%20Later%2C%20Buddhism%20reached%20foreign%20countries%20owing%20to%20the%20efforts%20of%20Ashoka.%20But%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Maurya%20dynasty%2C%20the%20ideology%20declined%20in%20Bihar.%20A%20major%20reason%20was%20the%20establishment%20of%20casteism%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20many%20castes%20including%20Kushwaha%2C%20Kurmi%2C%20Yadav%2C%20Kahar%2C%20Chamar%2C%20Paswan%2C%20and%20Pasi%20came%20into%20existence%20and%20society%20became%20fragmented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20aspects%20which%20are%20visible%20even%20today%20and%20are%20also%20recorded%20in%20government%20and%20non-government%20documents.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20recent%20report%20of%20the%20Bihar%20government%20shows%20that%20at%20present%20there%20are%20a%20total%20of%20209%20castes%20among%20which%20the%20Yadav%20caste%20has%20the%20largest%20population%2C%20that%20is%2C%201%2C86%2C50%2C119%20which%20is%2014.266%25%20of%20the%20total%20population.%20The%20enormous%20size%20of%20Yadav%20population%20has%20its%20advantages%20as%20well%20as%20disadvantages.%20One%20of%20the%20disadvantages%20is%20that%20many%20efforts%20have%20been%20made%20to%20Brahminise%20the%20Yadav%20caste%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20even%20though%20this%20caste%20has%20been%20pastoral%20in%20nature%20and%20in%20a%20way%20has%20tribalism%20at%20its%20core.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20historians%20and%20sociologists%2C%20be%20it%20R.S.%20Sharma%20or%20D.D.%20Kosambi%2C%20considered%20members%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20to%20be%20basically%20shepherds.%20Most%20people%20believe%20that%20as%20shepherds%20they%20made%20several%20discoveries%20which%20have%20not%20only%20enriched%20humanity%20but%20also%20brought%20people%20closer%20to%20knowledge%20and%20science.%20According%20to%20them%2C%20the%20shepherds%20were%20the%20first%20to%20discover%20which%20animal%20should%20be%20killed%20and%20eaten%20and%20whose%20milk%20is%20fit%20for%20drinking.%20However%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20denied%20that%20when%20agriculture%20developed%2C%20cattle%20rearing%20also%20started%20as%20the%20two%20activities%20complemented%20each%20other.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20contributions%20of%20shepherds%20have%20been%20highlighted%20historically%20in%20various%20ways.%20Such%20as%20in%20the%20figure%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%2C%20who%20may%20not%20have%20been%20born%20in%20a%20shepherd%20family%20but%20considered%20himself%20a%20shepherd.%20This%20is%20because%20he%20knew%20that%20only%20a%20shepherd%20could%20care%20for%20the%20voiceless.%20Their%20contribution%20in%20the%20development%20of%20human%20civilisation%20can%20also%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20form%20Islam%E2%80%99s%20Prophet%20Mohammed%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20shepherd.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20in%20India%2C%20shepherds%20were%20not%20considered%20only%20shepherds.%20They%20were%20known%20by%20various%20names%20such%20as%20Abhir%2C%20Ahir%2C%20Goala%2C%20or%20Gowar.%20Over%20time%2C%20they%20slowly%20came%20to%20be%20considered%20Hindus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20Aryans%20and%20non-Aryans%2C%20renowned%20historian%20Ramsharan%20Sharma%20writes%20in%20his%20famous%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Discovery%20of%20Aryan%20Culture%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CAfter%201800%20BC%2C%20Aryans%20entered%20India%20in%20small%20groups.%20The%20word%20Arya%20is%20found%20in%20both%20the%20oldest%20texts%2C%20Rigveda%20and%20Avesta.%20The%20word%20Iran%20is%20related%20to%20the%20word%20Arya.%20In%20the%20Rig%20Vedic%20period%2C%20those%20who%20worshiped%20Indra%20were%20called%20Aryans.%20According%20to%20some%20mantras%20of%20Rigveda%2C%20Aryans%20have%20their%20own%20separate%20caste.%20The%20people%20with%20whom%20they%20fought%20are%20described%20as%20black.%20The%20Aryans%20have%20been%20described%20as%20Manushi%20people%20who%20worshiped%20Agni%20Vaishwanar%20and%20sometimes%20set%20fire%20to%20the%20houses%20of%20black%20people.%20It%20has%20been%20said%20about%20the%20Aryan%20god%20Som%20that%20he%20used%20to%20kill%20black%20people.%20In%20post-Vedic%20literature%2C%20Arya%20meant%20those%20three%20varnas%20which%20were%20called%20Dwija.%20Shudras%20were%20not%20kept%20in%20the%20category%20of%20Aryans.%20Aryans%20were%20considered%20independent%20and%20Shudras%20were%20considered%20dependent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ERigveda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20main%20scripture%20of%20Aryan%20Brahmins%2C%20states%20that%20when%20Aryans%20came%20from%20Iran%2C%20they%20first%20encountered%20shepherd%20folk.%20You%20can%20also%20understand%20this%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ERigveda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20main%20king%20of%20the%20Aryans%20is%20Indra%20and%20of%20the%20total%2010%2C552%20verses%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ERigveda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20about%203%2C500%20verses%20are%20either%20related%20to%20Indra%20or%20dedicated%20to%20him.%20The%20eighth%20verse%20of%20the%20130th%20Sukta%20of%20the%20first%20Mandal%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3ERigveda%3C%2Fem%3E%20states%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndra%2C%20the%20protector%20(of%20his%20worship)%20battles%2C%20defends%20his%20%C4%80rya%20worshipper%20in%20all%20conflicts%2C%20in%20conflicts%20that%20confer%20heaven%3B%20he%20punished%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20his%20worshippers%20the%20neglecters%20of%20religious%20rites%3B%20he%20tore%20off%20the%20black%20skin%20of%20the%20aggressor%20named%20Krishna%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Anshumati%20river%20and%20killed%20him%20in%20a%20burning%20flame%2C%20he%20consumes%20him%20who%20delights%20in%20cruelty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20it%20is%20written%20in%20the%20first%20verse%20of%20the%20101st%20Sukta%20of%20the%20first%20Mandal%20of%20%3Cem%3ERigveda%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CGamatvijas%20offer%20adoration%20with%20oblations%20to%20him%20who%2C%20because%20of%20the%20friendship%20of%20King%20%E1%B9%9Aijishvan%2C%20destroyed%20the%20pregnant%20wives%20of%20K%E1%B9%9Bish%E1%B9%87a%3B%20desirous%20of%20protection%2C%20we%20invoke%2C%20to%20become%20our%20friend%2C%20him%20who%20holds%20the%20thunderbolt%20in%20his%20lustful%20right%20hand%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Maruts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20purported%20enmity%20with%20Indra%20extended%20from%20the%20Vedic%20era%20to%20the%20period%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EPuranas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20by%20then%20the%20Arya%20Brahmins%20had%20understood%20that%20killing%20Krishna%20(Krishna%20descendants)%20again%20and%20again%20would%20not%20work.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20Indra%20was%20no%20longer%20their%20chief%20king.%20The%20Aryans%20had%20established%20Vishnu%20for%20themselves.%20Apart%20from%20him%2C%20they%20had%20created%20gods%20like%20Shankar%20and%20Brahma.%20They%20also%20created%20goddesses.%20But%20Krishna%20was%20said%20to%20be%20superior%20to%20everyone.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20in%20%3Cem%3EMahabharat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Vedavyas%20depicted%20the%20defeat%20of%20Indra%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Krishna.%20But%20the%20matter%20does%20not%20end%20here.%20They%20went%20on%20to%20establish%20Krishna%20as%20the%20hero%20of%20%3Cem%3EMahabharat%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Chapter%2011%2C%20Verse%2041%2C%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EGita%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Arjuna%20says%2C%20%E2%80%98Thinking%20of%20You%20as%20my%20friend%2C%20I%20presumptuously%20addressed%20You%20as%2C%20%E2%80%9CO%20Krishna%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CO%20Yadav%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CO%20my%20dear%20Friend.%E2%80%9D%20I%20was%20ignorant%20of%20Your%20majesty%2C%20showing%20negligence%20and%20undue%20affection.%20And%20if%2C%20jestfully%2C%20I%20treated%20You%20with%20disrespect%2C%20while%20playing%2C%20resting%2C%20sitting%2C%20eating%2C%20when%20alone%2C%20or%20before%20others%20%E2%80%93%20for%20all%20that%20I%20crave%20forgiveness.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20sixteenth%20century%2C%20Tulsidas%20wrote%20in%20129%20(1)%20of%20Uttar%20Kand%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamcharitmanas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CListen!%20Oh%20foolish%20mind!%20Who%20has%20not%20attained%20supreme%20bliss%20by%20worshiping%20Shri%20Ram%20who%20purifies%20even%20the%20fallen%3F%20He%20defeated%20many%20evil%20people%20like%20Ganika%2C%20Ajamil%2C%20Vyadha%2C%20Geedh%2C%20Gaja%2C%20and%20others.%20I%20bow%20down%20to%20Shri%20Ram%2C%20whose%20name%20recited%20even%20once%20is%20sufficient%20to%20purify%20sinful%20beings%20like%20Abhir%2C%20Yavana%2C%20Kirat%2C%20Khas%2C%20Shvapach%20(Chandal)%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHence%2C%20Tulsidas%20in%20fact%20exposed%20the%20entire%20effort%20to%20paint%20the%20Yadavs%2C%20who%20are%20known%20by%20the%20nicknames%20Gwala%2C%20Gopa%2C%20Ahir%2C%20etc.%20in%20Bihar%2C%20in%20the%20colors%20of%20Hindutva.%20While%20they%20praise%20Krishna%20in%20Geeta%2C%20they%20consider%20Yadav%20people%20as%20sinful%20in%20Ramayana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20are%20present%20in%20many%20states%20of%20north%20India.%20They%20also%20reside%20in%20the%20southern%20states%20under%20different%20names.%20But%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%20the%20population%20of%20this%20caste%20is%20the%20highest.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20democratic%20politics%20is%20incomplete%20without%20their%20presence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20Bihar%2C%20their%20population%20is%20the%20highest%2C%20as%20mentioned%20before.%20While%20population%20is%20not%20everything%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20democratic%20politics.%20democracy%20did%20cause%20many%20miracles%20to%20happen%20in%20this%20country.%20For%20example%2C%20Mayawati%2C%20who%20was%20a%20Dalit%2C%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20while%20Rabri%20Devi%20was%20made%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F16191422%2F2022_8img16_Aug_2022_PTI08_16_2022_000116B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F16191422%2F2022_8img16_Aug_2022_PTI08_16_2022_000116B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F16191422%2F2022_8img16_Aug_2022_PTI08_16_2022_000116B-300x151.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F16191422%2F2022_8img16_Aug_2022_PTI08_16_2022_000116B-1024x514.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F16191422%2F2022_8img16_Aug_2022_PTI08_16_2022_000116B-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-614102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22602%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20with%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20HAM-S%20chief%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%20and%20RJD%20leader%20Rabri%20Devi%20during%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20of%20Bihar%20Cabinet%20Ministers%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20in%20Patna%2C%20August%2016%2C%202022.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20division%20among%20various%20gotras%20has%20also%20fragmented%20this%20caste%20due%20to%20which%20despite%20having%20a%20large%20population%2C%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20become%20a%20decisive%20political%20force.%20This%20can%20be%20understood%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20the%20Kurmi%20population%20in%20Bihar%20is%20only%203%2C762%2C969%20but%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20this%20caste%2C%20has%20been%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%20since%20December%202005.%20Due%20to%20the%20pressure%20of%20caste-based%20equations%2C%20it%20is%20understood%20that%20he%20had%20to%20make%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20the%20son%20of%20former%20chief%20ministers%20Lalu%20Prasad%20and%20Rabri%20Devi%2C%20his%20ally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20the%20politics%20of%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20was%20and%20still%20is%20incomplete%20without%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20Yadavs.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20B.P.%20Mandal%20was%20the%20first%20Yadav%20to%20become%20the%20chief%20minister%20followed%20by%20Daroga%20Prasad%20Rai.%20Later%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20also%20ruled%20Bihar%20from%201990%20to%201997%20and%20Rabri%20Devi%20from%201997%20to%202005.%20In%20the%20politics%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20names%20of%20Ramnaresh%20Yadav%2C%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20can%20be%20mentioned%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F238925%2Fbook-review-periyar-lalai-singh-granthawali%2F%5C%22%3EPeriyar%20Lalai%20Singh%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20challenged%20the%20Brahmin%20classes%2C%20is%20still%20relevant.%20He%20devoted%20his%20entire%20life%20to%20spread%20awareness%20among%20the%20deprived%20communities.%20He%20was%20the%20first%20person%20in%20North%20India%20who%20gave%20a%20new%20direction%20to%20the%20social%20movement%20by%20publishing%20the%20translation%20of%20Periyar%E2%80%99s%20classic%20work%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3A%20A%20True%20Reading%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Hindi%20under%20the%20title%20%3Cem%3ESachchi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20is%20not%20an%20exaggeration%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20Yadavs%20today%20are%20not%20following%20the%20path%20of%20Periyar%20Lalai%20Singh%20Yadav.%20They%20are%20now%20merely%20getting%20transformed%20into%20the%20ruling%20caste.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20also%20true%20that%20in%20both%20society%20and%20politics%2C%20they%20have%20posed%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20to%20the%20monopoly%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20castes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260830%2Fbihar-caste-survey-yadav-caste-society-politics%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20h