9033813%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Israel%20has%20denied%20any%20connection%20with%20the%20seized%20ship%2C%20unconfirmed%20reports%20suggest%20the%20ship%20may%20have%20an%20Israeli%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20officials%20insisted%20the%20ship%20was%20British-owned%20and%20Japanese-operated.%20However%2C%20ownership%20details%20in%20public%20shipping%20databases%20associated%20the%20ship%E2%80%99s%20owners%20with%20Ray%20Car%20Carriers%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20by%20Abraham%20%E2%80%9CRami%E2%80%9D%20Ungar%2C%20who%20is%20known%20as%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20men%20in%20Israel%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUngar%20denied%20comment%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20British%20military%E2%80%99s%20United%20Kingdom%20Maritime%20Trade%20Operations%2C%20which%20provides%20warnings%20to%20sailors%20in%20the%20Persian%20Gulf%20and%20the%20wider%20region%2C%20the%20hijacking%20occurred%20nearly%20150%20kilometers%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Yemen%E2%80%99s%20port%20city%20of%20Hodeida%2C%20near%20the%20coast%20of%20Eritrea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%20have%20repeatedly%20threatened%20to%20target%20Israeli%20ships%20in%20the%20waters%20off%20Yemen%20in%20wake%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20relentless%20bombing%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700464724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F17123254%2Fcontainer-ship-560789_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-alleges-houthi-rebel-hand-behind-hijacking-of-india-bound-cargo-ship-in-red-sea%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20was%20no%20immediate%20comment%20from%20the%20Houthis%2C%20an%20Iran-backed%20rebel%20movement%20in%20Yemen%20that%20had%20earlier%20threatened%20to%20target%20Israeli-linked%20vessels%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-alleges-houthi-rebel-hand-behind-hijacking-of-india-bound-cargo-ship-in-red-sea%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20the%20End%2C%20It%E2%80%99s%20Always%20XI%20Versus%20XI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20124329%2FF_TytKoWgAALbGm.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20we%20love%20sport%2C%20yes%3F%20Here%20we%20are%2C%20all%20set%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20coronation%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%2045-day%20pageant%20of%20self-celebration.%20The%20terraces%20are%20walls%20of%20blue.%20The%20skies%20are%20scored%20with%20patriotic%20jet%20trails.%20The%20boxes%20are%20full%20of%20puffed-up%20pooh-bahs%20and%20lotus-eating%20slebs.%20Oh%20look%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%2C%20in%20Narendra%20Modiland%2C%20with%20its%20ambitions%20for%20a%20Narendra%20Modiworld.%20Oh%20dear%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20spoiled%20by%20eleven%20happy-go-lucky%20Australians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENobody%20gave%20them%20a%20chance.%20Even%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20them%20much%20of%20one.%20India%20are%20just%20so%20good.%20A%20five-finger%20exercise%20I%20set%20myself%20during%20the%20World%20Cup%20was%20to%20pick%20a%20second%20Indian%20XI%20from%20players%20not%20in%20the%20first-choice%20team.%20You%E2%80%99d%20have%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20and%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Ravichandra%20Ashwin%20and%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Sanju%20Samson.%20Maybe%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%20to%20skipper%20and%20Umran%20Malik%20to%20bowl%20smoke.%20Crikey%2C%20they%E2%80%99d%20beat%20most%20international%20teams%3B%20they%E2%80%99d%20certainly%20flog%20the%20next-best%20Australians.%20By%20their%20abundance%20of%20talent%2C%20and%20by%20the%20game%E2%80%99s%20enjoying%20such%20precedence%2C%20India%20will%20always%20trade%20an%20advantage%20in%20the%20multi-format%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20always%20XI%20versus%20XI.%20It%E2%80%99s%20where%20Orwell%E2%80%99s%20timeworn%20%E2%80%98war%20minus%20the%20shooting%E2%80%99%20metaphor%20falls%20short%2C%20because%20the%20sporting%20battlefield%20is%20arbitrarily%20even%2C%20the%20forces%20are%20by%20consent%20restricted%2C%20and%20efforts%20at%20interference%20stand%20out%20%E2%80%93%20they%20can%20even%20be%20seen%20as%20slightly%20shameful.%20Prepare%20for%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20to%20argue%20that%20in%20view%20of%20their%20overwhelming%20contribution%20to%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20financial%20health%2C%20India%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20field%20fifteen%20players%20to%20everyone%20else%E2%80%99s%20eleven%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20to%20the%20final.%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20first%20glimmer%20is%20at%20the%20toss%2C%20affording%20Pat%20Cummins%20the%20opportunity%20to%20bat%20under%20the%20lights.%20Three%20of%20the%20four%20cup%20games%2C%20and%20both%20IPL%20finals%2C%20have%20been%20won%20by%20the%20pursuers%2C%20so%20the%20gamble%20seems%20worthwhile%3B%20nor%20is%20it%20so%20mercilessly%20hot%20that%2050%20overs%20in%20the%20field%20will%20be%20a%20punishment.%20Then%2C%20a%20tiny%20portent.%20Mitchell%20Starc%E2%80%99s%20second%20ball%20floats%20wide%20in%20search%20of%20shape%20back.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20thrashes%20and%20eyes%20swivel%20to%20the%20point%20boundary.%20But%20Travis%20Head%2C%20right%20where%20the%20data%20says%20he%20needs%20to%20be%2C%20tracks%20speedily%20left%20and%20saves%20two%20runs.%20And%20even%20as%20the%20Indians%20strain%20to%20get%20loose%2C%20they%20go%20on%20feeling%20an%20Australian%20check.%20At%20eight%20an%20over%2C%20they%20exceed%20their%20Cup%20power%20play%20average.%20But%20the%20Australian%20fielding%20probably%20saves%20a%20further%2020%20runs%2C%20and%20heralds%20the%20breakthrough%2C%20Head%20catching%20Rohit%2C%20running%20back%2C%20diving%20forward%2C%20celebrating%20perfunctorily.%20This%2C%20as%20Head%20described%20it%20later%2C%20was%20cricket%20in%20the%20best%20Australian%20vein.%20Thought%20he%20had%20no%20chance.%20Had%20a%20go%20anyway.%20Was%20surprised%20to%20catch%20it.%20Wasn%E2%80%99t%20inclined%20to%20make%20a%20fuss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20balls%20on%20from%20the%20Powerplay%2C%20India%20lose%20a%20third%2C%20and%20Australia%20are%20suddenly%20three%20further%20wickets%20from%20that%20invitingly%20elongated%20home%20tail%3A%20number%20eight%20Shami%2C%20whose%20highest%20score%20in%20100%20ODIs%20is%2025%3B%20number%20nine%20Bumrah%2C%20whose%20highest%20score%20in%2088%20ODIs%20is%2016.%20Sure%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20SKY%20to%20come%2C%20but%20he%E2%80%99s%20unproven%20in%20ODIs%2C%20and%20hardly%20a%20like-for-like%20swap%20with%20Hardik%20Pandya.%20So%2C%20now%20it%20is%20circumstances%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Australians%2C%20bearing%20down%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20fourth%20wicket%20partners.%20Cummins%20distributes%20the%20bowling%20load%20widely%3B%20the%20part-timers%20get%20off%20lightly%3B%20the%20fielding%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20overthrows%20aside%2C%20remains%20wonderfully%20vigilant.%20India%20find%20themselves%20in%20a%20game%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20while%20since%20they%20have%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20cameras%20dwell%20on%20Virat%20Kohli%E2%80%99s%20handsome%20features%20as%20he%20achieves%20his%20fifth%20consecutive%20score%20of%2050%20or%20more%2C%20the%20game%20has%20commenced%20an%20arc%20away%20from%20the%20hosts.%20Whether%20Kohli%20and%20K.L.%20Rahul%20spent%20too%20long%20over%20their%20runs%20will%20long%20be%20debated%3B%20after%20all%2C%20people%20still%20wonder%20whether%20Mike%20Brearley%20and%20Geoffrey%20Boycott%20spent%20too%20long%20over%20theirs%20in%20the%201979%20final.%20I%E2%80%99m%20more%20inclined%20to%20be%20forgiving%3A%20the%20design%20flaw%20of%20the%20order%20was%20always%20bound%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20India%20at%20some%20stage%2C%20likeliest%20of%20all%20in%20the%20final%20against%20the%20strongest%20opposition.%20Kohli%2C%20generally%20so%20decisive%2C%20seldom%20if%20ever%20drags%20on%20%E2%80%93%20a%20dismissal%20characteristic%20of%20conglomerated%20thoughts.%20Now%20he%20does%2C%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20with%20so%20little%20recent%20batting%2C%20is%20all%20at%20sea%20against%20the%20reversing%20ball.%20It%20all%20gets%20very%20messy%20until%20last-man-picked%20Marnus%20Labuschagne%20ends%20it%20with%20his%20fourth%20run%20out%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20it%E2%80%99s%20over%20to%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20other%20selection%20long%20shot%2C%20Head%2C%20included%20in%20the%20squad%20while%20still%20convalescent%2C%20and%20having%20gone%20six%20weeks%20without%20a%20hit%20before%20reappearing%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Dharamshala.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20dew%2C%20240%20is%20effectively%20210%3B%20thanks%20to%20Head%2C%20Australia%20take%2015%20off%20Bumrah%E2%80%99s%20first%20over.%20Australia%20are%20three%20down%20after%20seven%20overs%20but%20have%20already%20reduced%20the%20required%20run%20rate%20to%204.5.%20Shami%E2%80%99s%20lethality%20to%20left-handers%20does%20not%20prevent%20Head%20from%20picking%20two%20boundaries%20off%20him%20in%20the%20last%20over%20of%20the%20Powerplay%2C%20affording%20Labuschagne%20time%20to%20settle%20the%20way%20he%20likes%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20Head%20has%20a%2058-ball%20fifty%20by%20the%20time%20Labuschagne%20first%20finds%20the%20boundary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20all%20this%2C%20so%20further%20detail%20is%20probably%20superfluous.%20So%20let%E2%80%99s%20just%20concentrate%20on%20that%20brooding%20atmosphere%2C%20that%20eddying%20disbelief.%20When%20cricket%20and%20crowd%20feed%20off%20one%20another%20in%20India%2C%20there%20can%20be%20a%20feeling%20of%20playing%20against%20a%20whole%20country.%20Quiet%2C%20such%20as%20that%20now%20pervading%20Modi%20Stadium%2C%20is%20oppositely%20telling.%20The%20crowd%20know%20it.%20They%20ache%20to%20cheer%2C%20but%20cannot%20cajole%20themselves%20into%20doing%20so.%20As%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20and%20Labuschagne%20complete%20the%20winning%20run%2C%20the%20hush%20renders%20the%20cries%20from%20the%20Australian%20dugout%20audible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20realist%20could%20well%20argue%20that%20India%20won%20this%20World%20Cup%20anyway%3A%20they%20were%20able%20to%20round%20around%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cricket%20world%20like%20traffic%20cones%20for%20six%20weeks%3B%20they%20will%20rake%20off%20almost%20four%20in%20every%20ten%20dollars%20the%20tournament%20generated.%201983%20portended%20great%20cricket%20change%3B%202023%20confirms%20little%20more%20than%20that%20Australia%20is%20represented%20by%20an%20experienced%2C%20spirited%2C%20resourceful%20cricket%20team%2C%20that%20is%20even%20now%20coming%20to%20the%20end%20of%20its%20life%20cycle.%20The%20balance%20of%20global%20cricket%20power%2C%20politically%2C%20demographically%20and%20economically%2C%20is%20fundamentally%20undisturbed%3B%20the%20BCCI%20and%20BJP%20will%20remain%20separated%20by%20a%20fag%20paper%3B%20the%20international%20game%20will%20continue%20as%20an%20elite%20racket.%20Cricket%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%20had%20ten%20teams%20and%2048%20matches%3B%20football%E2%80%99s%20next%20World%20Cup%20will%20have%2048%20teams%20and%20104%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%E2%80%99ll%20be%20a%20satisfaction%20elsewhere%20today%20at%20India%20finishing%20second%20%E2%80%93%20the%20same%20satisfaction%20experienced%20when%20Australia%2C%20in%20its%20pomp%2C%20was%20bested%2C%20every%20so%20often%20(2001%20in%20India%2C%202005%20in%20England%20etc).%20Nobody%20now%20would%20remember%20the%20Titanic%20had%20it%20simply%20arrived%20in%20New%20York%3B%20India%20hitting%20an%20Australian%20iceberg%20is%20an%20infinitely%20superior%20sporting%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20today%20is%20as%20much%20a%20%E2%80%98birthplace%20of%20giants%E2%80%99%20as%20England%20ever%20was.%20Gandhi%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Nehru%2C%20Sardar%20Patel.%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%2C%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20Ravi%20Shankar%2C%20Mother%20Teresa.%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20can%20you%20hear%20me%3F%20Your%20boys%20took%20a%20hell%20of%20a%20beating!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fgideon-haigh%5C%22%3EGideon%20Haigh%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20a%20journalist%20for%20almost%20four%20decades%2C%20has%20published%20more%20than%2040%20books%20and%20contributed%20to%20more%20than%20100%20newspapers%20and%20magazines.%20He%20is%20also%20co-host%20of%20the%20podcast%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3ECricket%2C%20Et%20Cetera.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700464701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20124329%2FF_TytKoWgAALbGm.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-australia-cricket-world-cup-final-gideon-haigh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%E2%80%99s%20where%20Orwell%E2%80%99s%20timeworn%20%E2%80%98war%20minus%20the%20shooting%E2%80%99%20metaphor%20falls%20short.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-australia-cricket-world-cup-final-gideon-haigh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ChatGPT%20creator%20lands%20Microsoft%20job%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700462160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F70x70%2Fskynews-sam-altman-openai_6365600.jpg%3F20231119131324%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fno-immediate-return-to-openai-for-sam-altman-as-new-interim-ceo-appointed-13012044%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20interim%20chief%20executive%20has%20been%20appointed%20to%20the%20company%20behind%20major%20AI%20chatbot%20ChatGPT%2C%20with%20the%20ousted%20ex-CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20being%20tapped%20up%20to%20head%20a%20new%20Microsoft%20AI%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A68%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fno-immediate-return-to-openai-for-sam-altman-as-new-interim-ceo-appointed-13012044%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fno-immediate-return-to-openai-for-sam-altman-as-new-interim-ceo-appointed-13012044%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fno-immediate-return-to-openai-for-sam-altman-as-new-interim-ceo-appointed-13012044%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani-Hindenburg%3A%20Plea%20in%20SC%20Seeks%20Contempt%20Action%20Against%20SEBI%20for%20Delay%20in%20Completing%20Probe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F11165427%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_inside_bulidings_01.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0A%20petition%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20the%20initiation%20of%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20the%20market%20regulator%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20for%20failing%20to%20conclude%20its%20investigation%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fhindenburg-shorts-adani-group-flags-debt-and-accounting-concerns%5C%22%3Eallegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20stock%20manipulation%20and%20accounting%20fraud%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%20within%20the%20specified%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fplea-in-supreme-court-for-contempt-action-against-sebi-for-not-completing-probe-in-adani-hindenburg-matter-242513%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%3Cem%3E%20LiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20advocate%20Vishal%20Tiwari%2C%20one%20of%20the%20individuals%20who%20filed%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20(PIL)%20seeking%20a%20court-monitored%20inquiry%20into%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20the%20conglomerate%20by%20US-based%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research.%20Tiwari%20highlighted%20that%20according%20to%20the%20May%2017%20order%20of%20the%20top%20court%2C%20SEBI%20was%20required%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20by%20August%2014.%20However%2C%20the%20market%20regulator%20has%20not%20yet%20presented%20its%20final%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20sought%20a%20directive%20asking%20SEBI%20to%20explain%20its%20non-compliance%20and%20also%20the%20initiation%20of%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20the%20regulator.%20He%20also%20drew%20attention%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occrp.org%2Fen%2Finvestigations%2Fdocuments-provide-fresh-insight-into-allegations-of-stock-manipulation-that-rocked-indias-powerful-adani-group%5C%22%3Einvestigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%2C%20which%20also%20accused%20Adani%20Group%20companies%20of%20irregularities.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fadani-hindenburg-allegations-sc-appointed-panel-submits-report-in-a-sealed-cover%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court-appointed%20expert%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20also%20investigate%20the%20OCCRP%20report%2C%20Tiwari%20sought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20LiveLaw%2C%20while%20the%20scheduled%20hearing%20into%20the%20matter%20was%20on%20August%2029%2C%202023%2C%20the%20case%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20listed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Senior%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20had%20raised%20the%20matter%20before%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20on%20November%206%2C%20expressing%20urgency.%20The%20CJI%20assured%20that%20the%20issue%20would%20be%20examined%20with%20the%20registry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20two-month%20deadline%20set%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations%20raised%20by%20Hindenburg%20ended%20on%20May%202.%20SEBI%20requested%20an%20extension%2C%20citing%20the%20complexity%20of%20transactions%20and%20the%20need%20for%20additional%20time%2C%20and%20was%20granted%20time%20until%20August%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700461043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F11165427%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_inside_bulidings_01.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fadani-hindenburg-plea-supreme-court-contempt-sebi-delay-probe%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20application%20highlighted%20that%20according%20to%20the%20May%2017%20order%20of%20the%20top%20court%2C%20the%20market%20regulator%20was%20required%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20by%20August%2014.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fadani-hindenburg-plea-supreme-court-contempt-sebi-delay-probe%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Bayer%20Is%20Delivering%20Medical%20Care%20at%20the%20Doorsteps%20of%20Rural%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Bayer%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20rural%20healthcare%20system%20is%20strained%20due%20to%20a%20severe%20shortage%20of%20doctors%20and%20infrastructure.%20The%20Government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhmis.mohfw.gov.in%2Fdownloadfile%3Ffilepath%3Dpublications%2FRural-Health-Statistics%2FRHS%25202021-22.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ERural%20Health%20Statistics%202021-2022%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reveals%20a%20deficit%20of%2079.5%20percent%20in%20rural%20healthcare%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrimary%20Health%20Centres%20(PHC)%2C%20the%20initial%20point%20of%20care%20for%20villages%2C%20cater%20to%20around%2036%2C000%20people%20per%20PHC%2C%20as%20per%20the%20same%20report.%20PHCs%20typically%20have%20one%20medical%20officer%20who%20is%20a%20physician%2C%20staff%20nurses%2C%20and%20Auxiliary%20Nurses%20and%20Midwives%20(ANM)%20along%20with%20other%20staff%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInadequate%20infrastructure%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316087%2Fassam-couple-helps-rural-northeast-india-access-affordable-mental-healthcare-mita%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20patient%20load%3C%2Fa%3E%20contribute%20to%20significant%20stress%20on%20doctors%20and%20nurses.%20Villagers%20have%20to%20travel%20for%20about%2045%20minutes%20to%20reach%20the%20nearest%20district%20hospital%20to%20access%20a%20specialist.%20To%20address%20these%20issues%2C%20Bayer%20Foundation%20India%20(BFI)%20has%20established%20telemedicine%20centres%20at%20PHCs%20to%20bring%20top%20healthcare%20professionals%20to%20local%20communities%2C%20right%20at%20their%20doorstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarita%20Bahl%20%E2%80%94%20Country%20Group%20CSR%20Head%2C%20Bayer%2C%20South%20Asia%20%26amp%3B%20Director%2C%20Bayer%20Foundation%20India%20%E2%80%94%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20travelled%20to%20many%20districts%20across%20the%20country%20like%20Raichur%2C%20Khandwa%2C%20and%20Tikamgarh%2C%20and%20saw%20that%20there%20was%20very%20little%20support%20available%20in%20PHCs.%20People%20have%20to%20travel%20several%20kilometres%20just%20to%20see%20a%20specialist%2C%20and%20many%20may%20not%20go.%20So%20we%20realised%20that%20rather%20than%20building%20something%20new%2C%20we%20should%20make%20healthcare%20better%2C%20affordable%20and%20accessible%20right%20at%20the%20PHC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Bayer%20has%20set%20up%2028%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20telemedicine%20centres%20in%2014%20aspirational%20districts%20(a%20programme%20by%20the%20government%20to%20improve%20underdeveloped%20districts%20nationwide)%20across%20eight%20states%2C%20Sarita%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStrengthening%20the%20health%20index%20of%20the%20rural%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bayer's%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20consultation%20with%20specialists%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334462%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBayer%E2%80%99s%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20consultation%20with%20specialists.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBayer%E2%80%99s%20telemedicine%20centres%20set%20up%20within%20the%20PHCs%2C%20offer%20around%2020%20distinct%20medical%20specialities%20via%20teleconsultation.%20The%20centres%20include%20a%20trained%20GNM%20(General%20Nursing%20and%20Midwifery)%20and%20a%20centre%20coordinator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Sarita%20explains%2C%20when%20a%20patient%20requires%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316871%2Ffriends-launch-digiqure-teleconsultation-startup-affordable-rural-healthcare-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especialist%E2%80%99s%20opinion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20are%20directed%20to%20the%20telemedicine%20centre%2C%20often%20located%20in%20the%20adjacent%20room%20within%20the%20PHC.%20Here%2C%20the%20nurse%20links%20the%20patients%20to%20the%20specialist%20via%20a%20video%20call%20after%20examining%20their%20vital%20signs%20and%20medical%20background.%20Post%20the%20consultation%2C%20the%20nurse%20issues%20a%20printed%20prescription%20to%20the%20patient%2C%20who%20can%20purchase%20the%20prescribed%20medications%20from%20the%20PHC%20pharmacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20easy%20access%20to%20doctors%20to%20villagers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334464%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20easy%20access%20to%20doctors%20to%20villagers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFalguni%2C%20the%20ANM%20at%20the%20Phygital%20in%20Chhiri%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20emphasises%20the%20significant%20benefits%20that%20Bayer%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20has%20brought%20to%20the%20local%20community%20and%20nearby%20villages.%20She%20highlights%20that%20patients%20from%20remote%20villages%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20endure%20the%20trouble%20of%20travelling%20and%20spending%20an%20entire%20day%20at%20the%20district%20hospital.%20With%20the%20convenience%20of%20accessing%20various%20specialists%20through%20telemedicine%20centres%2C%20patients%20have%20readily%20embraced%20this%20solution.%20She%20notes%20that%20their%20PHC%20witnesses%20over%2090%20teleconsultation%20cases%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Hanifa%20Batterywala%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20doctor%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTelemedicine%20helps%20us%20reach%20even%20remote%20areas%20where%20often%20patients%20are%20daily%20wage%20workers%20who%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20lose%20an%20entire%20day%20to%20travel%20to%20see%20a%20doctor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20suffering%20from%20chronic%20itching%20for%20two%20months%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20the%20ANM%2C%20Falguni%2C%20and%20she%20booked%20a%20video%20consultation%20with%20a%20dermatologist.%20The%20doctor%20prescribed%20a%20lotion%20and%20a%20medicine.%20My%20itching%20reduced%20in%20just%20three%20to%20four%20days%2C%20and%20I%20have%20faced%20no%20problem%20after%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sonal%20Patel%2C%20a%20patient%20from%20Chirri.%20Falguni%20adds%20that%20most%20patients%20seek%20help%20for%20skin%20allergies%20or%20paediatric%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20limited%20timings%20of%20the%20PHCs%2C%20Bayer%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20centres%20operate%20from%20nine%20to%20five%2C%20providing%20access%20to%20physicians%2C%20gynaecologists%2C%20cardiologists%2C%20ENT%20specialists%2C%20dermatologists%2C%20paediatricians%2C%20and%20other%20experts%20via%20teleconsultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDiagnosing%20silent%20killers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bayer%20conducts%20several%20awareness%20camps%20in%20rural%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334466%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBayer%20conducts%20monthly%20health%20camps%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20non-communicable%20diseases.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBayer%E2%80%99s%20analysis%20of%20data%20collected%20from%20all%20the%20PHCs%20suggested%20that%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20cases%20at%20the%20centres%20constituted%20non-communicable%20diseases%20(NCDs)%20such%20as%20hypertension%20and%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20prevalence%20of%20diabetes%20and%20hypertension%20is%20rapidly%20increasing%2C%20as%20indicated%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1944600%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20ICMR-INDIAB%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20estimates%20the%20numbers%20to%20be%20101%20million%20and%20136%20million%2C%20respectively.%20The%20study%20also%20highlights%20that%20more%20than%20one-third%20of%20Indians%20are%20affected%20by%20hypertension%2C%20with%20a%20high%20prevalence%20of%20prediabetes%20observed%20in%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322755%2Fkarnataka-divaa-uthkarsha-project-surya-type-one-diabetes-awareness-for-underprivileged-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDiabetes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20associated%20NCDs%20can%20lead%20to%20cardiovascular%20complications%20and%20other%20health%20issues%20such%20as%20kidney%2C%20foot%2C%20and%20eye%20diseases.%20The%20report%20emphasises%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20early%20diagnosis%2C%20prevention%20and%20treatment%20to%20reduce%20fatalities%20caused%20by%20these%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20these%20tenets%20is%20a%20major%20part%20of%20Bayer%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20today.%20They%20organise%20monthly%20health%20camps%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20diabetes%2C%20hypertension%2C%20various%20heart%20conditions%2C%20breast%20cancer%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarita%20informs%20that%20since%20April%202022%2C%20they%20have%20organised%20over%20539%20health%20camps%2C%20reached%206%2C000%20villages%2C%20and%20assisted%20over%201%2C70%2C000%20beneficiaries%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20These%20camps%20involved%20over%2095%2C000%20general%20consultations%20and%2074%2C000%20specialist%20consultations.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20no%20disease%20goes%20undiagnosed%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20resources%20or%20awareness.%20Quality%20health%20care%20should%20be%20available%20to%20every%20person%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sarita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700460854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bayer%20Foundation%20India%20(BFI)%20has%20set%20up%2028%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20telemedicine%20centres%20in%20villages%20of%208%20states%20to%20provide%20easy%20access%20to%20quality%20medical%20care.%20It%20is%20also%20conducting%20health%20camps%20for%20early%20diagnosis%20of%20breast%20cancer%2C%20hypertension%20and%20diabetes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334461%2Fbayer-foundation-telemedicine-healthcare-centres-diabetes-hypertension-rural-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asked%20by%20O.P.%20Jindal%20University%20to%20'Express%20Regret%2C'%20Achin%20Vanaik%20Stands%20by%20Lecture%20on%20Palestine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20105752%2F7005574091_4292365d6d_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Critically%20acclaimed%20writer%20and%20former%20Delhi%20University%20professor%20Achin%20Vanaik%2C%20whose%20recent%20lecture%20on%20Palestine%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20University%20got%20mired%20in%20controversy%2C%20has%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fscholar-stands-by-his-lecture-at-op-jindal-university-regrets-its-misinterpretation%2Farticle67551383.ece%5C%22%3Ehe%20stands%20by%20his%20lecture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana-based%20private%20university%20had%20asked%20Vanaik%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexpress%20regret%E2%80%9D%20over%20his%20remarks%20during%20a%20closed%20lecture%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20History%20and%20Politics%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Present%E2%80%99%20held%20on%20November%201.%20Vanaik%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20had%20informed%20the%20university%20he%20stood%20by%20what%20he%20had%20said%20in%20the%20lecture%2C%20and%20regretted%20its%20misinterpretation%20and%20the%20confusion%20that%20had%20arisen%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20lecture%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Naor%20Gilon%20had%20written%20to%20the%20founding%20vice-chancellor%20university%2C%20C.%20Raj%20Kumar%2C%20saying%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20understand%20why%20an%20event%20delegitimising%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20was%20hosted%20at%20the%20University.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%E2%80%99s%20registrar%2C%20Dabiru%20Sridhar%20Patnaik%2C%20subsequently%20wrote%20to%20Vanaik%20on%20November%2013%2C%20saying%20that%20his%20remarks%20on%20Hindutva%20and%20it%20being%20anti-Muslim%20were%20unnecessary%20and%20objectionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Findia-israel-palestine-kashmir-azad-ressa%5C%22%3EIn%20State%20Repression%20and%20Its%20Justification%2C%20India%20and%20Israel%20Have%20Much%20in%20Common%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVanaik%20said%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20prioritise%20one%20particular%20community%2C%20this%20is%20in%20contrast%20with%20another%20conception%20of%20nationalism%2C%20which%20in%20India%20is%20that%20of%20composite%20nationalism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20many%20had%20recorded%20his%20lecture%20on%20Palestine%20and%20posted%20some%20parts%20online.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20that%20I%20am%20pro-terrorism%20is%20absolute%20nonsense.%20My%20words%20were%20absolutely%20taken%20out%20of%20context%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20want%20to%20clarify%20here%20that%20I%20do%20consider%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20action%20as%20a%20terrorist%20action%20and%20criticise%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Bombay%20had%20cancelled%20Vanaik%E2%80%99s%20proposed%20talk%20expected%20to%20throw%20light%20on%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20and%20the%20repercussions%20of%20the%20recent%20violence%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fjindal-university-achin-vanaik-israel-palesti