0settled%20in%20the%20area.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20spent%20some%20time%20in%20Alaska%20and%20knew%20the%20way%20an%20Igloo%20is%20made.%20He%20gave%20us%20an%20idea%20of%20how%20the%20science%20behind%20the%20construction%20works%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFurthermore%2C%20we%20used%20the%20internet%20extensively%20to%20understand%20the%20process.%20I%20also%20used%20YouTube%20to%20see%20how%20people%20live%20in%20them%20and%20how%20sustainable%20they%20are%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20climate%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-15-at-1.20.46-PM-1-1700142360-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334307%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVinod%20has%20hosted%20hundreds%20of%20guests%20at%20his%20igloos.%20Picture%20Credit%3A%20Vinod%20Bodh%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202017%2C%20the%20Igloos%20were%20up%20and%20ready%20to%20use.%20%E2%80%9CI